It also provides H.V. equipment, including metal enclosed switchgears, RMU, metal clad switchgears, MV switches and disconnectors, concrete kiosk, mobile substation, and HV live-tank circuit breakers. The company was incorporated in 1983 and is based in Sincan, Turkey.

stocks.name: Atakey Patates Gida Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.

It also provides frozen cheese stick and onion rings. It supplies its products to quick service restaurants. It also exports to China, Brazil, Iraq, and United Arab Emirates. Atakey Patates Gida Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. was incorporated in 2012 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: ATP Yazilim ve Teknoloji Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: ATP Yazilim ve Teknoloji Anonim Sirketi, together with its subsidiaries, develops enterprise software and system solutions in Turkey, the Netherlands, Malta, China, Europe, the Middle East, and Africa. The company offers restaurant POS, customer experience, O2O and delivery, restaurant management, and MDM and support center services under the Zenia brand; brokerage software, portfolio management, RPA and automation, mobile and virtual branch, finance applications, and market connectivity solutions under the Tradesoft brand; CRM, ERP and e-accounting, custom business solutions, and corporate support services under the Digital brand; green and carbon certificates trading under the GreenX brand; and  autonomous robots under the RobotX brand. It also provides cloud computing and artificial intelligence solutions; business solutions, including ERP, CRM, and BI ve HR, e-transformation, BPM and low-code, capital markets, and robotic; infrastructure and security solutions, such as netsec, data security, and threat and system management; system solutions comprising database, switchboard, data leak prevention, payment and barcode, and UPS systems; and IT services, which include licensing, integration, and research and development consultancy, as well as managed, professional, and field services. It serves hospitality, finance, retail, energy, and logistics sectors. The company was formerly known as ATP Ticari Bilgisayar Agi ve Elektrik Guc Kaynaklari Uretim Pazarlama ve Ticaret A.S. and changed its name to ATP Yazilim ve Teknoloji Anonim Sirketi in April 2023. ATP Yazilim ve Teknoloji Anonim Sirketi was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Akin Tekstil Anonim Sirketi

The company offers cotton and blend, wool, real indigo, corduroy, linen, garment dye, and yarn dyed fabrics; men's and women's trousers and bermudas; and women's shirts, dresses, skirts, blouses, and other products. It exports its products. Akin Tekstil Anonim Sirketi was founded in 1956 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

Its products include sun dried tomatoes, oven semi dried tomatoes, sauces and bruschettas, fermented vegetables, and grilled products. The company serves hotels, restaurants, and the catering industry, as well as retail chains. It also exports its products. A.V.O.D Kurutulmus Gida ve Tarim Ürünleri Sanayi Ticaret Anonim Sirketi was founded in 2003 and is based in Izmir, Turkey.

stocks.name: Ayen Enerji A.S.

Ayen Enerji A.S. is a subsidiary of Aydiner Insaat AS.

stocks.name: Balatacilar Balatacilik Sanayi Ve Ticaret A.S.

stocks.name: Bizim Toptan Satis Magazalari A.S.
stocks.description: Bizim Toptan Satis Magazalari A.S. engages in the wholesale and retail of fast-moving consumer goods in Turkey. The company sells food products, including dry food, milk and diary, snack and bakery, delicatessen and breakfast, meat and meat products, and fruit and vegetable; drink and non-alcoholic beverages; cigarette and tobacco; cleaning items; personal care and cosmetics; paper; household appliances; energy and lighting, stationery-office supplies; communication items; pet products; and private label products through various brands. It also operates 182 stores and an online platform. The company sells its products to wholesalers, merchants, grocery stores, markets, supermarkets, specialized retailers, hotels, restaurants, and cafes, as well as gas station markets, school canteens, SEC Market business partners, kiosks, catering businesses, corporate and individual customers, and commercial taxpayers. Bizim Toptan Satis Magazalari A.S. was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. The company operates as a subsidiary of Yildiz Holding A.S.

stocks.name: Bilici Yatirim Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Bilici Yatirim Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. engages in the textiles, tourism, and energy businesses in Turkey. The company is involved in the production of textiles, fabrics, cloths, dyeing, finishing, and sizing operations or outsourcing; and semi-finished products and raw materials, including cotton gin, pressed sawdust, and yarn, as well as various clothing made of cotton fabric and polyester. It also engages in buying, renting, constructing buildings; tourism activities; and electricity production. Bilici Yatirim Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. was founded in 1950 and is based in Adana, Turkey.

stocks.name: Bms Celik Hasir Sanayi Ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Bms Celik Hasir Sanayi Ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi operates in the steel business. The company manufactures and trades in steel mesh, cold drawn bar iron, high carbon steel wire, cold drawn coil, galvanized wire, knitting wire, fencing wire, stirrups, kilt, and ready-made iron products. Bms Celik Hasir Sanayi Ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi was founded in 1971 and is based in Manisa, Turkey.

stocks.name: Bms Birlesik Metal Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Bms Birlesik Metal Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. manufactures and sells galvanized steel wires in Turkey and internationally. The company offers hot-dip galvanized, Zn-AI coated steel, stranded, and black annealed wires. It serves the automotive, energy, agriculture, construction, environmental protection and security system, construction, and industrial application sectors. The company also exports its products to approximately 45 countries, including Europe, North American, and South American countries. Bms Birlesik Metal Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. was founded in 1968 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Bantas Bandirma Ambalaj Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Bantas Bandirma Ambalaj Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. engages in tin packaging production activities in Turkey. The company offers cheese cans; oil cans for olive and vegetable oil companies; olive and pickle tin boxes; and thinner, antifreeze, and motor oil cans. It also serves the mineral oil and paint industries. The company exports its products to various countries. The company was incorporated in 1986 and is headquartered in Balikesir, Turkey.

stocks.name: Bogazici Beton Sanayi Ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Bogazici Beton Sanayi Ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi produces, manufactures, and sells ready-made concrete and aggregates under the Bosphorus Concrete brand in Turkey. It offers standard concretes; special and technical concretes, such as fiber reinforced, colored, pressed concrete, ready plaster, screed, concrete with visible aggregate surface, white, and impermeable concretes; and boutique concretes for industrial field, marine structure, and construction and precast production sites. Bogazici Beton Sanayi Ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Borlease Otomotiv A.S.
stocks.description: Borlease Otomotiv A.S. offers car rental services in Turkey. It provides fleet leasing and management, mobility, implant and fuel management, and vehicle and driver support services. The company was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: BOR SEKER
stocks.description: Bor Seker A.S. manufactures and sells sugar products in Turkey. It offers granulated sugar, sugar cubes, stick sugar, wet beet pulp, bagged beet pulp, and molasses. The company was founded in 1983 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Bossa Ticaret ve Sanayi Isletmeleri T.A.S.
stocks.description: Bossa Ticaret ve Sanayi Isletmeleri T.A.S., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the manufacturing, marketing, and sale of textile products in Turkey. It also offers various denim products. The company was incorporated in 1951 and is headquartered in Adana, Turkey.

stocks.name: Berkosan Yalitim Ve Tecrit Maddeleri Üretim Ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Berkosan Yalitim Ve Tecrit Maddeleri Üretim Ve Ticaret A.S. engages in the manufacture, import, and export of insulation and insulation materials in Turkey and internationally. The company offers flat-bonded polyethylene, polypropylene and cross-linked polyethylene foam for sectors, such as construction, automotive, packaging, installation, shoes, and bags. It also provides a range of services, such as interstory screed application, to wall and roof insulation; soundproofing and thermal insulation in parquet to refrigerated cooler vehicle insulation; air conditioning inside and outside tools to sound and vibration isolation; heat and noise prevention in mechanical installations; and sound and vibration absorbing band. In addition, the company offers heat and sound insulation; solar energy system isolation; split air-conditioning system isolation; heating system isolation; and wastewater system isolation. It provides its products under the Foamex, Airpack, Polyberk, Proberk, Airfoam, and Reflekt X brand names. The company was incorporated in 1993 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Birikim Varlik Yonetim Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Birikim Varlik Yonetim Anonim Sirketi operates as an asset management company in Turkey. The company engages in the purchase and sale of receivables and other assets of banks, private financial institutions, and other financial institutions; collection of purchased receivables from the debtor; and development, sale, operation, and leasing of real estate or other goods. It also provides consultancy and intermediary services in restructuring the receivables and other assets of banks and other financial institutions; restructuring and improvement activities, including additional financing and capital to customers; and consultancy services to companies in the areas of corporate and financial restructuring. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey. Birikim Varlik Yonetim Anonim Sirketi operates as a subsidiary of Altinhas Yatirim Holding A.S.

stocks.name: Birlik Mensucat Ticaret ve Sanayi Isletmesi A.S.
stocks.description: Birlik Mensucat Ticaret ve Sanayi Isletmesi A.S. supplies and sells finished cloth in Turkey. The company offers towels, home textiles, and bedding products under the SOLEY brand. The company was incorporated in 1966 and is headquartered in Kayseri, Turkey.

stocks.name: Borusan Birlesik Boru Fabrikalari Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.address: Pürtelas Hasan Mah. Meclisi Mebusan Caddesi No: 35-37
stocks.description: Borusan Birlesik Boru Fabrikalari Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. manufactures, produces, and sells steel pipes in Turkey. It offers spiral (helical) welded pipes, HSAW, LSAW and ERW line pipes, natural gas pipes, boiler tubes, industrial pipes and profiles, water pipes, construction pipes and profiles, SRM installation pipes, hydraulic cylinder tubes, cold drawn pipes, advanced processed pipes, precision pipes and profiles, and OCTG pipes. The company also exports its products. It serves water, construction, industrial, automotive, and energy applications. The company was formerly known as Borusan Mannesmann Boru Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. and changed its name to Borusan Birlesik Boru Fabrikalari Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. in November 2023. The company was incorporated in 1958 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. Borusan Birlesik Boru Fabrikalari Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. is a subsidiary of BMB Holding A.S.

stocks.name: Batisöke Söke Çimento Sanayii T.A.S.
stocks.description: Batisöke Söke Çimento Sanayii T.A.S. manufactures and sells clinker and cement products in Turkey and internationally. The company offers portland cement clinkers and potassium silicate cement; portland, sulphate resistant portland, portland compound, and pozzolanic cement; and aggregates and cement bypass dust. It exports its products. The company was founded in 1955 and is headquartered in Izmir, Turkey. Batisöke Söke Çimento Sanayii T.A.S. operates as a subsidiary of Batiçim Bati Anadolu Çimento Sanayii Anonim Sirketi.

stocks.name: Batiçim Bati Anadolu Çimento Sanayii Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Batiçim Bati Anadolu Çimento Sanayii Anonim Sirketi operates in the cement industry in Turkey and internationally. The company offers Portland cement clinkers and potassium silicate cements; Portland, sulphate resistant Portland, Portland compound, and pozzolanic cements; and aggregate and cement bypass dust products. Batiçim Bati Anadolu Çimento Sanayii Anonim Sirketi was founded in 1966 and is headquartered in Izmir, Turkey.

stocks.name: Burçelik Bursa Çelik Döküm Sanayii A.S.
stocks.description: Burçelik Bursa Çelik Döküm Sanayii A.S. engages in the steel casting and machinery manufacturing businesses in Turkey and internationally. The company offers stationary crushing and screening plants, such as jaw, impacts, cone crushers, sieves, sand machine, vertical shaft breakers, hammer breakers, and supplementary equipment that includes bunkers and feeders, conveyor belts, products silos, automation systems, and washers; and mobile crushing and screening units comprising mobile jaw, impact, and cone crushers, as well as mobile sieve and padder. It also manufactures and sells hydromechanical components, including voltage, suction pipe, inlet pipe, etc. that operate under high pressure for hydroelectric power plants; ship container crane jibs, adapters, and ship loading facilities for the shipbuilding industry; and mineral crushers, jaw crushers, cone crushers, rotor crushers, mobile crawler crushers, and steel casting spare parts for the mining industry. In addition, the company provides machining and welding products. Its products are used in automotive, iron and steel production, cement, power generation, marine, industrial valve, heavy construction machinery, industrial machinery, and mining and crushers industries. The company was founded in 1968 and is headquartered in Bursa, Turkey.

stocks.name: Burçelik Vana Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Burçelik Vana Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. engages in the production of casting, machinery , and industrial valves in Turkey and internationally. The company offers wafer, lug, double flanged, two piece PTFE, and vulcanized seat lug butterfly valves; flanged 2 piece, monoblock wafer type, two/three piece threaded, geothermal, floating / trunnion flanged, welded oil and gas, top entry, threaded / socket weld class 800, and double block and bleed ball valves; cast steel, forged, knife, and rubber sealing gate valves; and casted and forged globe valves. It also provides flanged / welded swing, forged steel threaded / socket weld swing, flanged / welded piston, forged steel threaded / socket weld piston, dual plate wafer / lug type, wafer swing, and spring wafer check valves; lubricated / nun-lubricated flanged and PFA lined flanged plug valves; sanitary strainers, sanitary butterfly, and sanitary check valves; and diaphragm valves, as well as T and Y type strainers. In addition, the company offers electric and pneumatic actuators, limit switch and gear boxes, selenoid valves, and positioners. The company was founded in 1968 and is headquartered in Nilüfer, Turkey.

stocks.name: Bulbuloglu Vinc Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi
stocks.address: Organize Sanayi Bölgesi, Oguz Cad. No:21
stocks.description: Bulbuloglu Vinc Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi manufactures and sells cranes and custom-designed machinery. It offers travelling cranes, gantry cranes, process cranes, lifting groups, jib cranes, and crane equipment, as well as provides technical services, spare parts, control, and inspection services for the steel, energy, automotive, shipyards and ports, mining, and industrial production industries. Bulbuloglu Vinc Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi was founded in 1985 and is headquartered in Ankara, Turkey.

stocks.name: Baydoner Restoranlari A.S.
stocks.description: Baydoner Restoranlari A.S. operates and franchises a chain of restaurants in Turkey and Iraq. The company was founded in 2007 and is based in Izmir, Turkey.

stocks.name: Çan2 Termik A.S.
stocks.description: Çan2 Termik A.S. engages in the generation and sell of electricity in Turkey. It operates thermal power plant with an installed capacity of 340 MWm/330 Mwe. The company is involved in renting of coal-based electrical energy production facilities. It also engages in the mining business. The company was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. Çan2 Termik A.S. is a subsidiary of Odas Elektrik Üretim Sanayi Ticaret A.S.

stocks.name: Casa Emtia Petrol Kimyevi ve Turevleri San. Tic. A.S.
stocks.description: Casa Emtia Petrol Kimyevi ve Turevleri San. Tic. A.S. engages in trading of commodities in Turkey. The company trades in physical goods such as oil, gold, and agricultural products. It offers gasoline, diesel, and fuel oil products; and operates six fuel stations. The company was founded in 1976 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: CATES ELEKTRIK
stocks.description: Çates Elektrik Üretim Anonim Sirketi engages in the production and sale of electricity through its thermal power plant. It also involve in the maintenance and repair work on site. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is based in Mugla, Turkey.

stocks.name: Coca-Cola Içecek Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Coca-Cola Içecek Anonim Sirketi, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the production, sale, and distribution of sparkling and still beverages in Turkey, Pakistan, Bangladesh, Central Asia, and the Middle East. The company offers soft drinks, fruit juice, iced teas, water and sparkling water, sports and energy drinks, and coffee. It sells its products under the Coca-Cola, Coca-Cola Zero Sugar, Coca-Cola Light, Diet Coke, Fanta, Sprite, Sprite Zero Calories, Crush, Crystal Cola, Schweppes, Fusetea, Cappy, Piko, Damla, Damla Minera, Bon Aqua, Al Waha, Arwa, Dasani, Dasani Minera, Kinley, Kinley Soda, Power Ade, Monster Energy, Burn, Roar, Predator Energy, and Costa Coffee brands. Coca-Cola Içecek Anonim Sirketi was founded in 1964 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Çelik Halat ve Tel Sanayii A.S.
stocks.description: Çelik Halat ve Tel Sanayii A.S. produces and supplies steel wire ropes and wires worldwide. The company offers steel wire ropes, such as general purpose ropes, plastic coated core wire ropes, rotation resistant wire ropes, non-rotation resistant wire ropes, marine and mining ropes, pre-stretched elevator wire ropes, fishery and forestry ropes,  and oil and gas ropes that are used in the construction, maritime, fishing, oil, mining and in elevators, chair lifts, and cranes. It also provides industrial steel, industrial galvanized steel, and patented wires for use in the automotive, white goods, agriculture, defense industry, furniture, and construction sectors. In addition, the company offers pre-stressed and post-tensioned bridge beam manufacturing, prefabricated building elements, ground and mine anchors, nuclear power plants, silo construction, and residential and commercial building construction sectors. The company was incorporated in 1962 and is based in Izmit, Turkey. Çelik Halat ve Tel Sanayii A.S. is a subsidiary of Artas Insaat Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.

stocks.name: Çemas Döküm Sanayi A.S.
stocks.description: Çemas Döküm Sanayi A.S. provides alloyed grinding products for the cement and mining industries. It offers grinding media balls and cylpebs. The company also produces cast parts, nodular and grey iron, and machining parts for use in the agriculture, automotive, construction and machinery, white goods, pumps, reducers, and machineries, such as knuckle, reducer housing, axle housing, transmission housing, weight, transmission parts, wheel hubs, oil sump, brake disc, reducer housing cover, flywheel, gearbox, cover, crankshaft pulley, axle components, engine cap, flywheel housing, agricultural ancillary equipment, brake discs and brake levers, suspension components, gear sets and gearboxes, differential components, exhaust manifolds, transmission housing parts, pistons, brackets, engine components, seat plates, brake drums, flywheels, control arms, differansiyel parçalari, crane load-bearing parts, housing, bearing housing, and fittings. Çemas Döküm Sanayi A.S. was incorporated in 1976 and is based in Kirsehir, Turkey.

stocks.name: Ceo Event Medya A.S.
stocks.description: Ceo Event Medya A.S. engages in the event management business in Turkey and internationally. The company conducts openings, seminars, symposiums, meetings, and concerts and campaigns, as well as organizes events for private or public offices, institutions, and organizations in various fields and subjects. It is also involved in congress, entertainment, sports, fair, design, and corporate event management. The company was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. Ceo Event Medya A.S. operates as a subsidiary of Yeni ve Eski Medya Reklam Ajansi A.S.

stocks.name: Cimbeton Hazir Beton ve Prefabrik Yapi Elemanlari Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi
stocks.address: Isiklar Mah. Eski Kemalpasa Cad. No:5
stocks.description: Cimbeton Hazir Beton ve Prefabrik Yapi Elemanlari Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the production, sale, trade, and transportation of cement, ready-mixed concrete, bulk and bagged cement, and lime in Turkey. The company was founded in 1950 and is based in Izmir, Turkey. Cimbeton Hazir Beton ve Prefabrik Yapi Elemanlari Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi operates as a subsidiary of Cimentas Izmir Cimento Fabrikasi Turk A.S.

stocks.name: Çimentas Izmir Çimento Fabrikasi Türk A.S.
stocks.description: Çimentas Izmir Çimento Fabrikasi Türk A.S., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the production, trading, sale, and transportation of bulk and bagged cement in Turkey. The company operates through four segments: Cement, Aggregate, Ready-mixed concrete, and Waste management. It is involved in the sale of fuels; and fly ash production business. The company was founded in 1947 and is headquartered in Izmir, Turkey. Çimentas Izmir Çimento Fabrikasi Türk A.S. is a subsidiary of Aalborg Portland Espana SL.

stocks.name: Consus Enerji Isletmeciligi ve Hizmetleri A.S.
stocks.description: Consus Enerji Isletmeciligi ve Hizmetleri A.S. operates as an energy service company in Turkey. The company operates biomass power plants with a total installed capacity of 34.2 MW; and cogeneration, trigeneration, and solar plants totaling 59.3 MW. Consus Enerji Isletmeciligi ve Hizmetleri A.S. was incorporated in 2014 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey. Consus Enerji Isletmeciligi ve Hizmetleri A.S. is a subsidiary of Global Yatirim Holding A.S.

stocks.name: Cosmos Yatirim Holding Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Cosmos Yatirim Holding Anonim Sirketi, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the purchase, sale, trade, loading, unloading, storage, and distribution of petroleum and petroleum derivative products in Turkey. The company also purchases and sells paintings, sculptures, and works of art, as well as carries out related commercial activities. In addition, it draws mechanical, electrical, and construction projects; participates in construction contracting works; constructs and sells residences, workplaces, and commercial buildings; purchases lands to build buildings; and provides engineering and architectural services. Further, the company installs hospital rooms, operating rooms, laboratories, clean rooms, and air conditioning systems; establishes monitoring and control rooms in subways, stadiums, and hospitals, and performs maintenance and repair of the installed systems. Additionally, it produces and sells electrical and electronic automated, distribution, and medium voltage and low current panels for industrial facilities, energy facilities, shopping malls, and hospitals. It also takeovers, transfers, operates, operates, and franchising shops of wholesale and retail purchase; and engaged in sale, distribution, import and export of hamburgers and hamburger by-products, and materials. The company was formerly known as Cosmos Yatirim Ortakligi AS and changed its name to Cosmos Yatirim Holding Anonim Sirketi in December 2013. Cosmos Yatirim Holding Anonim Sirketi was incorporated in 1995 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Creditwest Faktoring Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Creditwest Faktoring Anonim Sirketi provides factoring services for domestic and international transactions. The company was formerly known as Creditwest Faktoring Hizmetleri A.S. and changed its name to Creditwest Faktoring Anonim Sirketi in July 2012. The company was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: CarrefourSA Carrefour Sabanci Ticaret Merkezi A.S.
stocks.description: CarrefourSA Carrefour Sabanci Ticaret Merkezi A.S. engages in the retail business in Turkey. The company has hypermarket, supermarket, and franchises. It also engages in the leasing of real estate properties. The company was incorporated in 1991 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. CarrefourSA Carrefour Sabanci Ticaret Merkezi A.S. operates as a subsidiary of Haci Ömer Sabanci Holding A.S.

stocks.name: Cuhadaroglu Metal Sanayi ve Pazarlama A.S.
stocks.description: Cuhadaroglu Metal Sanayi ve Pazarlama A.S. manufactures and sells aluminum doors and windows in Turkey and internationally. It offers doors and window, sliding, and facade systems; automatic sliding and revolving doors, and KTS glazed folding door systems, as well as glass accessories; office partition systems; and fire and bullet proof joinery systems, and bomb resistant facades. The company sells its products under the Interal, Interax, Interwall, Intersecure, and Interdigi brands. Cuhadaroglu Metal Sanayi ve Pazarlama A.S. was founded in 1954 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: CVK Maden Isletmeleri Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: CVK Maden Isletmeleri Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi engages in production, marketing and sale of chrome, marble, lead, zinc, copper, silver, gold, and magnesite ores. The company was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: CW Enerji Mühendislik Ticaret ve Sanayi Anonim Sirketi
stocks.address: Antalya Organize Sanayi Bölgesi 1. Kisim Atatürk Bulvari No:20
stocks.description: CW Enerji Mühendislik Ticaret ve Sanayi Anonim Sirketi operates in the photovoltaic power generation sector in Turkey. The company offers inverters comprising hybrid and irrigation inventors, solar irrigation cabinets, off and on grid inventors, and accessories; MPPT and PWM charge controllers; solar infrastructure and solar connection equipment; solar panels; heating and cooling related equipment; energy storage and solar lighting solutions; and electric vehicle chargers. It also provides solar packs, such as boat/yacht packages, micro inverter balcony sets, carport packages, agricultural irrigation packages, on-grid packages, solar umbrella, solar jacket, and solar bank. In addition, the company provides solar-power irrigation systems, off-grid and on-grid solutions, solar powered camera systems and signages, and Led lighting system services, as well as technical and maintenance services. CW Enerji Mühendislik Ticaret ve Sanayi Anonim Sirketi was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Antalya, Turkey.

stocks.name: Dagi Giyim Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Dagi Giyim Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S., together with its subsidiary, produces, markets, and retails ready-to-wear products for men, women, and kids in Turkey and internationally. The company primarily produces and sells underwear, pajamas, nightgowns, tracksuits, plus size, maternity clothes, and swimsuits and swim shorts. It also offers casualwear, including T-shirt, crop tops/tanks, shorts, sweatshirt/jacket, pants, sweatpants, dress, shirt, and maternity casual wear; home-sleepwear; beachwear, such as bikini, bikini tops and bottoms, beach dress, mayokini, and pareo; and sportswear. In addition, the company provides accessories, such as lingerie and hair accessories, socks, sunglasses, bag, towel, slippers, hat, and beanie. It sells its products through online, retail stores, wholesale channels, and franchises. Dagi Giyim Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. was founded in 1984 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: DAP Gayrimenkul Gelistirme A.S.
stocks.description: DAP Gayrimenkul Gelistirme A.S. engages in the real estate business in Turkey. It is involved in the construction and development of residences, office, commercial, business centers, holiday villages, hotels, schools, and private hospital projects. The company was incorporated in 1981 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Dardanel Onentas Gida Sanayi A.S.
stocks.description: Dardanel Onentas Gida Sanayi A.S. engages in the seafood business in Turkey and internationally. The company is involved in the production and sale of canned food, including tuna, salmon, sardines, mackerel, anchovy, and other seafood; frozen food comprising mussels and other seafood; and fish by-products, such as fish meal and oil. Dardanel Onentas Gida Sanayi A.S. was incorporated in 1981 and is headquartered in Çanakkale, Turkey.

stocks.name: Denge Yatirim Holding A.S.
stocks.description: Denge Yatirim Holding A.S. operates in the logistics, real estate, and technology sectors in Turkey and internationally. The company is involved in the production of motion pictures, TV series, documentaries, advertisements, videos, and television programs for national and international cinema, television, and digital broadcasting platforms. It also provides integrated port services; transportation services, such as FTL  LTL, micro distribution, and fleet; and storage services. In addition, the company engages in the sales, distribution, and after-sales services for computer and peripheral products. Further, it offers access, network, and security solutions, as well as financial services. Additionally, the company engages in construction contracting activities, such as engineering and architecture, project development, housing, and business center production. Denge Yatirim Holding A.S. was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Derluks Yatirim Holding Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Derluks Yatirim Holding Anonim Sirketi, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and retails leather, textile, knitwear, and weaving products for men, women, and children in Turkey and internationally. It also manufactures clothing accessories; trades leather and textile chemicals, fabric, yarn, and apparel materials; and distributes and markets water, soft drinks, alcoholic and non-alcoholic beverages, and food products. In addition, it produces and sells electricity through solar energy sources. The company was formerly known as Derluks Deri Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi and changed its name to Derluks Yatirim Holding Anonim Sirketi in March 2021. Derluks Yatirim Holding Anonim Sirketi was incorporated in 2002 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Derimod Konfeksiyon Ayakkabi Deri Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Derimod Konfeksiyon Ayakkabi Deri Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. provides leather and fashionable products for men and women in Turkey. Its products include leather jackets and coats, briefcases, bags, clutch and portfolio products, socks, care products, backpacks, card holder, belts, wallets, and socks care products, as well as sneakers, boots, casual and classic shoes, loafers, espadrilles, sandals, slippers, heels, and ballerians. The company also operates stores. Derimod Konfeksiyon Ayakkabi Deri Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. was incorporated in 1975 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Desa Deri Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Desa Deri Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. manufactures and sells leather and leather products in Turkey. It offers leather jackets, clothing, shoes, bags and accessories, backpacks, suitcases, and other leather accessories for men and women. The company markets and sells its products through wholesale and retail sales channels, as well as through online store. It also exports its products. The company was founded in 1972 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. Desa Deri Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. is a subsidiary of Çelet Holding A.S.

stocks.name: Despec Bilgisayar Pazarlama ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Despec Bilgisayar Pazarlama ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi distributes information technology consumables to the computer companies in Turkey and internationally. The company offers phones, computer and tablet accessories, printer consumables, home systems, security cameras, mobile device accessories, and data storage products, as well as toner, ink cartridges, ribbons, backup products, paper products, and accessories. The company was formerly known as Indeks Teknolojik Ürünler Dagitim A.S. and changed its name to Despec Bilgisayar Pazarlama ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi in October 1998. The company was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Deva Holding A.S.
stocks.description: Deva Holding A.S. manufactures, markets, and sells pharmaceutical products in Turkey. The company offers antineoplastic and immunomodulating agents; dermatological products; sysyemic hormanal preparations; anti-infective and antiparasitic products for systemic use; food supplements; and electrolyte solutions. It also provides products in the areas of urogenital system and sex hormones, blood and blood forming organs, cardiovascular system, musculoskeletal system, nervous system, alimentary tract and metabolism, respiratory system, urinary systems, connective tissue, and sensory organs. In addition, the company offers various products in sterile and non-sterile forms, including liquids, semi-solids, solids, cephalosporins, penicillin, hormone and inhalation products, solid and liquid oncology, animal health products, active pharmaceutical ingredients, ampoules, liquid and lyophilized vials, eye drops, medical ampoules for sterile injectable products, and cologne. It also exports its products to approximately 60 countries. The company was incorporated in 1958 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey. Deva Holding A.S. is a subsidiary of Eastpharma S.à R.L.

stocks.name: Datagate Bilgisayar Malzemeleri Ticaret Anonim Sriketi

It provides smart phones, computer, tablets, modems, notebooks, and smart phone accessories, as well as security, wearable technology, smart life product, artificial technologies, modems, and virtual reality products, as well as smart phone accessories. The company was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. Datagate Bilgisayar Malzemeleri Ticaret Anonim Sriketi operates as a subsidiary of Indeks Bilgisayar Sistemleri Mühendislik Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi.

stocks.name: Dogus Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S.
stocks.description: Dogus Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. (Company) has been incorporated in accordance with capital market law on 25 July 1997. Dogus Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S.'s (the Company) which is traded on the Borsa Istanbul, main activity is to invest in properties, create, manage, make the necessary changes in the portfolio, minimize the risk of variation in real estate; property related capital market instruments, invest and monitor continuously the real estate based projects and take the necessary measures to protect, also research to increase the value of the portfolio. The headquarter of the Company is registered in Dogus Center Maslak, Maslak Mahallesi Ahi Evran Cad. No: 4/23 Maslak, Sariyer-Istanbul.

stocks.name: Doganlar Mobilya Grubu Imalat Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi

stocks.description: Doganlar Mobilya Grubu Imalat Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi engages in the manufacture and sale of furniture in Turkey. It manufactures and markets a range of furniture products for living rooms, bedrooms, dining rooms, youth rooms, kitchen, and bathrooms, as well as beds. The company also offers accessories, lighting, decorative items, garden furniture, and home textiles. It provides its products under the Dogtas, Kelebek, Lova Sleep, Kelebek Kitchen & Bathroom, Ruum Store, and Biga Home brand names. The company was formerly known as Dogtas Kelebek Mobilya Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. and changed its name to Doganlar Mobilya Grubu Imalat Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi in January 2022. Doganlar Mobilya Grubu Imalat Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi was incorporated in 1935 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Diriteks Dirilis Tekstil Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Diriteks Dirilis Tekstil Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S., together with its subsidiaries, produces and sells blankets and non-slip carpets in Turkey. Its products include single, double, and baby blankets. The company is also involved in provision of marketing services; and manufacture of yarn used in blanket and carpet production. Diriteks Dirilis Tekstil Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. was incorporated in 1996 and is based in Isparta, Turkey.

stocks.name: Ditas Dogan Yedek Parça Imalat ve Teknik A.S.
stocks.description: Ditas Dogan Yedek Parça Imalat ve Teknik A.S. manufactures and sells steering and suspension parts for vehicle manufacturers in Turkey and internationally. It offers rod ends, torque and V-torque rods, idler arms, axial joints, pitman arms, drag links, ball joints, track control arms, and stabilizer links for commercial vehicles and passenger cars. The company was incorporated in 1972 and is based in Nigde, Turkey. Ditas Dogan Yedek Parça Imalat ve Teknik A.S. operates as a subsidiary of BDY Group Insaat A.S.

stocks.name: Demisas Döküm Emaye Mamülleri Sanayi Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Demisas Döküm Emaye Mamülleri Sanayi Anonim Sirketi engages in the manufacture and sale of iron, cast iron, enameled products, enameled cast iron vessels, and other products in Turkey. It offers Volan, air brake disc, pressure plate, campane, bracket, shaft arm, manifolt, and caliper body products. The company provides its products for the white goods and automotive industries. It also exports its products to Germany, Belgium, the Czech Republic, France, Holland, England, Spain, Italy, Hungary, Poland, Romania, Russia, Slovakia, and Tunisia. The company was incorporated in 1974 and is headquartered in Kocaeli, Turkey.

stocks.name: Dinamik Isi Makina Yalitim Malzemeleri Sanayi Ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Dinamik Isi Makina Yalitim Malzemeleri Sanayi Ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi engages in the marketing and partial production of insulation hanger pins, plastic dowels, and cold room nails in Turkey. The company offers polyethylene sheets, pipes, and wicks; XLPE foam insulation products, including dynafoam XPE, adhesive, and aluminum coated crosslinked polyethylene foams; XPS foam insulation products, such as dynafoam XPS under tile thermal boards, frigo panel sheets, thermal insulation boards, decorative brick coating, and sandwich panel sheets; dynaflex rubber sheets and pipes; and specially designed products. It also provides mineral fiber products comprising glass, rock, and ceramic wools; pyramid shaped foam used in interior surface applications, industrial areas, radio and recording studios, entertainment venues, conference halls, generator rooms, compressors, and waiting rooms and acoustic viol; and packaging products, including insulated cold chain packaging, packaging profiles, and corner protectors. In addition, it offers joint filler rovings; PVC insulaton covering boards; and jackets valves and PVC insulation jackets. The company was incorporated in 1991 and is based in Izmir, Turkey.

stocks.name: Dogus Otomotiv Servis ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Dogus Otomotiv Servis ve Ticaret A.S., together with its subsidiaries, engages in automotive and real estate businesses in Turkey. It operates through automotive and real estate segments. The automotive segments engages in the importing, marketing, and selling vehicles, spare parts, and marine engines of Volkswagen Group brands VW, Audi, Seat, Cupra, Porsche, Bentley, Lamborghini, Meiller, Scania, Wielton semi-trailers, and Thermoking vehicle cooling systems; purchasing and selling used vehicles through dealers under the DOD brand; sales and service of Novamarine brand boats and speedboats, as well as after-sales services and spare parts field; and sales and service operations of Aerofoil brand e-foil products and Mate brand electric-assisted bicycles. The real estate segment operates a portfolio consisting of real estate-based assets and rights. It also offers installation and operation of charging units, charging stations, and charging network; and create and manage a portfolio of real estate and real estate-based capital market instruments. The company was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. Dogus Otomotiv Servis ve Ticaret A.S. operates as a subsidiary of Dogus Holding A.S.

stocks.name: DO & CO Aktiengesellschaft
stocks.description: DO & CO Aktiengesellschaft provides catering services in Austria, Turkey, Great Britain, the United States, Spain, Germany, and internationally. It operates through three divisions: Airline Catering; International Event Catering; and Restaurants, Lounges & Hotel. The company offers airline catering services; and event catering, infrastructure, and planning services. The company also engages in the operation of lounges, retail stores, airport catering, restaurants and Demel café, hotels, and staff restaurants. It operates restaurants and cafes under the DO & CO, Hédiard, HENRY, AIOLI, and Demel brands. The company was founded in 1981 and is headquartered in Vienna, Austria.

stocks.name: Dofer Yapi Malzemeleri Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Dofer Yapi Malzemeleri Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. manufactures and sells iron, steel mesh, and reinforcing bar products in Turkey. It offers cold drawing rods and pipe ducts, as well as prefabricated, reinforced concrete structure, and concrete transformer substation mesh products. Dofer Yapi Malzemeleri Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. was incorporated in 1985 and is headquartered in Ankara, Turkey.

stocks.name: Dogusan Boru Sanayii ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Dogusan Boru Sanayii ve Ticaret A.S. engages in the commercialization and industrial activities related to Roman-type perlite concrete tiles and perlite floor tiles in Turkey. It sells tiles, pallets, and pipes made of perlite. The company was founded in 1974 and is headquartered in Erzincan, Turkey.

stocks.name: Döktas Dökümcülük Ticaret ve Sanayi A.S.
stocks.description: Döktas Dökümcülük Ticaret ve Sanayi A.S. produces and trades gray and spheroidal cast iron, and aluminum castings for the automotive industry in Turkey. The company operates through Pig & Ductile Iron Casting; Aluminum Casting; and Wheels segments. It offers pig and ductile iron; aluminum cast parts; and aluminum wheels. The company also exports its products. It serves the automotive, heavy commercial vehicles, construction, and agricultural machinery industries. The company was formerly known as Componenta Dökümcülük Ticaret ve Sanayi A.S. and changed its name to Döktas Dökümcülük Ticaret ve Sanayi A.S. in April 2018. The company was incorporated in 1973 and is based in Bursa, Turkey. Döktas Dökümcülük Ticaret ve Sanayi A.S. is a subsidiary of Çelik Holding A.S.

stocks.name: Duran Dogan Basim ve Ambalaj Sanayi A.S.
stocks.description: Duran Dogan Basim ve Ambalaj Sanayi A.S., together with its subsidiaries, provides packaging products in Turkey, Europe, the United Stated, the Middle East, Africa, the Asia Pacific, and internationally. It provides paper, cardboard, and various plastic materials in rolls and sheets to produce various packaging, printing, chiseling, cutting, gluing, and laminating works on aluminum, metal, tin, etc. The company offers packaging products for food, boutique, medical, home and personal care, and boutique sectors. Duran Dogan Basim ve Ambalaj Sanayi A.S. was founded in 1934 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: DYO Boya Fabrikalari Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: DYO Boya Fabrikalari Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. produces and sells paints, varnishes, resins, other surface coatings, and construction and thermal insulation products in Türkiye and internationally. It offers construction paints, furniture paints, industrial paints, defense industry paints, coil coatings, automotive repair paints, marine paints, powder coatings, protective coatings, thermal insulation systems, and unsaturated polyester resins. The company was founded in 1927 and is headquartered in Izmir, Türkiye. DYO Boya Fabrikalari Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. is a subsidiary of Yasar Holding A.S.

stocks.name: Deniz Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S.
stocks.description: Deniz Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. operates as a real estate investment trust in Turkey. The company engages in real estate investment and development activities. Its property portfolio consists of residential, hotel, and commercial units in Istanbul, Ankara, and Bodrum. The company qualifies as a real estate investment trust for federal income tax purposes. It generally would not be subject to federal corporate income taxes if it distributes at least 90% of its taxable income to its stockholders. The company was incorporated in 1995 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. Deniz Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. is a subsidiary of Denizbank Anonim Sirketi.

stocks.name: EIS Eczacibasi Ilaç, Sinai ve Finansal Yatirimlar Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.

The Health segment is involved in the production, marketing, and sale of medicines related to human health and veterinary medicines. The Real Estate Development segment develops real estate properties; engages in rental activities for serum facilities; and provides consulting services on land development and project management. The company was incorporated in 1951 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey. EIS Eczacibasi Ilaç, Sinai ve Finansal Yatirimlar Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. is a subsidiary of Eczacibasi Holding A.S.

stocks.name: Eczacibasi Yatirim Holding Ortakligi A.S.

It also provides guiding and informative presentation, exhibition, consultancy, sales, and after-sales services. In addition, the company engages in real estate development; reference and generic pharmaceutical, nuclear medicine, real estate, and ceramic coating markets; leasing offices and shopping centers; and general investment activities. The company was incorporated in 1973 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. Eczacibasi Yatirim Holding Ortakligi A.S. is a subsidiary of Eczacibasi Holding A.S.

stocks.name: E-Data Teknoloji Pazarlama Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: E-Data Teknoloji Pazarlama Anonim Sirketi engages in the distribution of technology products and solutions to institutions and organizations in Turkey. It offers network products, printing solutions, cyber security products, server-storage products, data center infrastructure products, and other hardware and software solutions, as well as endpoint and data security solutions. The company also provides technical consultancy, installation, and other pre- and post-sales services. It offers its solutions to telecommunication, finance, insurance, manufacturing, health, education, entertainment, and other industries, as well as in SMB market. E-Data Teknoloji Pazarlama Anonim Sirketi was founded in 2008 and is based in Ankara, Turkey.

stocks.name: Edip Gayrimenkul Yatirim Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.

It also engages in the organization services, and marketing and operations, as well as trades, rents, leases, and sells real estate properties. Edip Gayrimenkul Yatirim Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. was formerly known as Edip Iplik Sanayi veTicaret A.S. and changed its name to Edip Gayrimenkul Yatirim Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. in June 2009. Edip Gayrimenkul Yatirim Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. was incorporated in 1971 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Ege Endüstri ve Ticaret A.S.

stocks.name: Nasmed Özel Saglik Hizmetleri Ticaret Anonim Sirketi

The company offers medical treatments and healthcare services to individuals and organizations. Nasmed Özel Saglik Hizmetleri Ticaret Anonim Sirketi was incorporated in 2003 and is based in Izmir, Turkey.

The company also provides nitrogenous compounds and fertilizers, and organic solvents. In addition, it sells petroleum products. The company was incorporated in 1973 and is based in Izmir, Türkiye.

stocks.name: Ege Profil Ticaret ve Sanayi Anonim Sirketi

stocks.name: Ege Seramik Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Ege Seramik Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. produces and sells floor and wall tiles worldwide. The company also provides glazed porcelain and colorful masse. Ege Seramik Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. is a subsidiary of Ibrahim Polat Holding A.S.

stocks.name: Ekiz Kimya Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi

The company was formerly known as Ekiz Yag ve Sabun Sanayii A.S. and changed its name to Ekiz Kimya Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. in September 2014. Ekiz Kimya Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi was founded in 1946 and is headquartered in Izmir, Turkey.

The company also resells products of energy sector. It serves power producers, network operators, and industrial and commercial consumers. The company was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Balikesir, Turkey.

stocks.name: Eksun Gida Tarim Sanayi Ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi

It offers various flours, such as bread, multipurpose, wholegrain, wafer, biscuit, cake, sandwich, sliced bread, and Atbazar products. The company offers various flour under the Sinangil and Gluten Yok brands. It exports its products to the Far East, Latin America, Africa, and the Middle East. The company was incorporated in 1996 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. Eksun Gida Tarim Sanayi Ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi operates as a subsidiary of Eksim Yatirim Holding A.S.

stocks.name: Elite Naturel Organik Gida Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Elite Naturel Organik Gida Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S., together with its subsidiaries, produces and sells organic fruits and vegetables in Turkey and internationally. The company offers juices, pulps, concentrates, semi-finished products, and finished forms of foodstuffs, as well as carbonated, non-carbonated, and non-alcoholic beverages. It exports its products to approximately 30 countries. The company was founded in 1975 and is headquartered in Ankara, Turkey.

stocks.name: Emek Elektrik Endustrisi Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Emek Elektrik Endustrisi Anonim Sirketi engages in the production, testing, marketing, and sale of transformers, capacitors, separators, and electromechanical equipment in Turkey and internationally. It offers oil type and epoxy resin current and voltage transformers, and disconnectors. The company was incorporated in 1969 and is based in Ankara, Turkey. Emek Elektrik Endustrisi Anonim Sirketi operates as a subsidiary of Emek Elektrik USA Inc.

stocks.name: Eminis Ambalaj Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Eminis Ambalaj Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. engages in the manufacture and sale of plastic and metal products in Turkey and internationally. The company offers plastic products, including bucket, heavy bucket, performance bucket, light bucket, and can products; and can, spout can, drum, putty can, diameter box, bucket, and bottom ring metal products. Its products are used in paint and chemical, mineral oil, construction chemicals, pool chemicals, confectionery, marmalade and chocolate, powder beverage, and cosmetics industries. Eminis Ambalaj Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. was incorporated in 1970 and is based in Dilovasi, Turkey.

stocks.name: Enerya Enerji Anonim Sirketi

The company also offers operational and consultancy services, as well as engages in precious metal mining. It serves residential and industrial customers. Enerya Enerji Anonim Sirketi was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. Enerya Enerji Anonim Sirketi is a subsidiary of Ahlatci Dogal Gaz Dagitim Enerji ve Yatirim A.S.

stocks.name: Ensari Sinai Yatirimlar Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Ensari Sinai Yatirimlar Anonim Sirketi, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and sells leather products in Turkey. The company offers merino, merinillo, lacoon, toscana, rassado, tigrado, French, and domestic UK products. It also produces, sells, imports, and exports raw materials, products, machinery, and facilities related to the flour industry; and provides paper and cardboard, PVC, cellophane, polyethylene, polypropylene, plastic materials, aluminum, metal, and tinplate, etc., as well as offers printing, gluing, and laminating services. In addition, the company generates electricity through renewable energy sources. The company was formerly known as Ensari Deri Gida Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. and change its name to Ensari Sinai Yatirimlar Anonim Sirketi in June 2025. Ensari Sinai Yatirimlar Anonim Sirketi was incorporated in 1993 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Egeplast Ege Plastik Ticaret ve Sanayi Anonim Sirketi

The company also provides sprinkler irrigation systems and drip irrigation systems. Its products are used in buildings, clean water distribution, sewerage, telecommunications, natural gas, drainage, infrastructure, and similar areas. The company was incorporated in 1973 and is based in Izmir, Turkey.

stocks.name: Erbosan Erciyas Boru Sanayii ve Ticaret A.S.

The company also provides industrial tubes and hollow sections for use in automotive, home appliances, furniture, greenhouse, construction, and transportation industries, as well as fence, industry and building, textile, and solar energy systems. In addition, it offers square, rectangular hollow sections and low-pressure boiler and steam pipes. Erbosan Erciyas Boru Sanayii ve Ticaret A.S. was incorporated in 1974 and is headquartered in Kayseri, Turkey.

stocks.name: Erciyas Çelik Boru Sanayi A.S.
stocks.description: Erciyas Çelik Boru Sanayi A.S. engages in the manufacture and sale of steel pipes in Turkey. It offers natural gas, oil pipes, and water pipes. The company was incorporated in 1990 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Ersu Meyve ve Gida Sanayii A.S.
stocks.description: Ersu Meyve ve Gida Sanayii A.S. manufactures and sells concentrates and pulp juices from fruits in Turkey. The company offers concentrate products; puree concentrate; puree/pulp; NFC fruits juice; tomato paste; organic products; fruit juices; fruit nectars; fruit juice drinks; and flavored drinks. It also exports its products. The company serves retail sales points, as well as military facilities, hospital cafes, schools and sport complexes, catering, etc. Ersu Meyve ve Gida Sanayii A.S. was founded in 1968 and is based in Konya, Turkey.

stocks.name: Escar Filo Kiralama Hizmetleri A.S.
stocks.description: Escar Filo Kiralama Hizmetleri A.S. provides motor vehicle rental services in Turkey. It offers various services, including vehicle delivery, financing support, roadside assistance, tire management, backup vehicle, door-to-door, online fleet reporting, and related consulting services, as well as insurance brokerage services. The company was incorporated in 2001 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Escort Teknoloji Yatirim A.S.

The company develops mobile and computer games, and application software; develops safe driving and accident prevention system for mobile platforms; creates an operating system to combat climate change and sustainability under the Ekofoni brand; operates online sports and sports facilities and trainers; operates cosmetic laboratories; develops software for financial technologies; operates blockchain technology platform; and produces solar-based renewable energy. It also offers artificial intelligence-based recruitment management system under the brand OneNewOne name; video analysis services; curriculum-based training and book contents of experts; consultation application for physicians; social media content management platform to corporate and individual users; data analytics, scouting, and team management platform services for e-sports organizations; beauty and care products; insight and forecasting tools; online marketplace platform for commercial loans; medical device for the treatment of glaucoma and neurological disorders; management software; online consultancy services to parents; IoT products and solutions; business intelligence and enterprise solutions; payment and e-commerce solutions; consumer electronics; and after-sales services for automotives. In addition, the company produces nickel-based cathodes for secondary batteries, and develops software for use in battery materials, as well as engages in venture investment activities. Escort Teknoloji Yatirim A.S. was founded in 1991 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Esenboga Elektrik Üretim A.S.

The company owns solar power plants; and involved in solar power plant contracting business. It also provides operation and maintenance solutions; and project development and turnkey EPC services. Esenboga Elektrik Üretim A.S. was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Ankara, Turkey. Esenboga Elektrik Üretim A.S. is a subsidiary of Naturel Yenilenebilir Enerji Ticaret A.S.

stocks.name: Etiler Gida Ve Ticari Yatirimlar Sanayi Ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Etiler Gida Ve Ticari Yatirimlar Sanayi Ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi operates restaurants, patisseries, tea gardens, cafeterias, coffee houses, and buffets in Turkey. It offers kebabs, wraps, doners, versions, portions, snacks, wraps, burgers, toasts, cold and hot sandwiches, breakfast, cold drinks, freshly squeezed fruit juices, desserts, and salads. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Euro Trend Yatirim Ortakligi A.S.
stocks.description: Euro Trend Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. manages the portfolio of capital market instruments. It monitors the developments related to securities, financial markets, institutions, and partnerships for portfolio management. The company was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Ankara, Turkey.

stocks.name: Euro Yatirim Holding A.S.
stocks.description: Euro Yatirim Holding A.S. engages in the provision of financial services in Turkey. The company offers brokerage services, including stock trading transactions, foreign currency securities, futures and options market brokerage transactions, as well as repo and reverse repo transactions; public offering intermediation; and investment consulting services. It also provides portfolio management services and TEFAS fund transactions. Euro Yatirim Holding A.S. was incorporated in 1996 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Euro Kapital Yatirim Ortakligi Anonim Sirketi

The company monitors developments in securities, financial markets, institutions, and partnerships, and distributes investment risk through portfolio diversification. It also offers portfolio management services and conducts research to protect and enhance the value of the portfolio. The company was founded in 2011 and is based in Ankara, Turkey.

stocks.name: Europower Enerji ve Otomasyon Teknolojileri Sanayi Ticaret Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Europower Enerji Ve Otomasyon Teknolojileri Sanayi Ticaret Anonim Sirketi designs, develops, manufactures, and sells electrical system products in Turkey. The company offers medium and low voltage products, compact substations, PFC systems, railway products, silicone insulators, as well as oil type distribution, medium power, and special type transformers. It also provides various services, such as project design, project management, automation and scada, supervision, and training services. In addition, the company offers laboratory and field tests, measurement, analysis and reporting of electrical power, as well as engineering and commissioning services. Further, it also undertakes electrical and electromechanical EPC projects in Turkey and internationally. The company was founded in 2008 and is based in Ankara, Turkey.

stocks.name: Europen Endustri Insaat Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Europen Endustri Insaat Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. engages in the manufacturing and sale of PVC window and door profiles in Turkey. It also offers PVC sheets and panels; and refrigerator, oven, furniture, and solar panel glasses. The company was founded in 1965 and is headquartered in Eskisehir, Turkey.

stocks.name: Euro Menkul Kiymet Yatirim Ortakligi Anonim Sirketi

The company was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Ankara, Turkey.

stocks.name: Eyg Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S.
stocks.description: Eyg Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. operates as a real estate investment trust. The company was founded in 2014 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Fade Gida Yatirim Sanayi Ticaret Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Fade Gida Yatirim Sanayi Ticaret Anonim Sirketi engages in the food business. It operates through Agricultural, Shopping Center, and Construction segments. The company provides salted/sulphured sun-dried tomatoes; frozen or dried fruits and vegetables; and manages shopping centers, as well as sells interior decoration and other construction activities. It sells its organic products worldwide. The company was incorporated in 1995 and is headquartered in Izmir, Turkey.

stocks.name: Fenerbahçe Futbol A.S.
stocks.address: Fenerbahçe Sükrü Saraçoglu Stadium Marathon Entrance
stocks.description: Fenerbahçe Futbol A.S. operates football club in Turkey. The company operates in Football Activity and Retailing segments. It distributes, markets, and sells Fenerbahce licensed products through stores, corners, and website. The company was founded in 1907 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey. Fenerbahçe Futbol A.S. is a subsidiary of Fenerbahçe Spor Kulübü.

stocks.name: Flap Kongre Toplanti Hizmetleri Otomotiv ve Turizm A.S.
stocks.description: Flap Kongre Toplanti Hizmetleri Otomotiv ve Turizm A.S. plans and organizes events and meetings under the Flap Tour brand name for the tourism industry. It organizes product launch meetings, education meetings, dealers' meetings, and corporate opening organizations. The company is also involved in organizing press meetings and bulletins; and the preparation of the printed materials for presentations. In addition, it offers association management services, such as general management and secretariat, membership succeeding, course and seminar organizations, finance and budget management, and Web services; and IT and graphic design services, including logo and visual projects for congress and meetings, design and printing of printed materials, online abstract module software, electronic poster module software, congress registration and accommodation module software, and internal use web server and customizable software options. Further, the company provides ticketing services; tracks payments and contracts of the hotel projects; and governmental organizational, national medical congress, and international medical congress services. Flap Kongre Toplanti Hizmetleri Otomotiv ve Turizm A.S. was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Ankara, Turkey.

stocks.name: Federal-Mogul Izmit Piston Ve Pim Üretim Tesisleri A.S.
stocks.description: Federal-Mogul Izmit Piston Ve Pim Üretim Tesisleri A.S. manufactures and trades in pistons and pins in Turkey. It also manufactures and trades liners, rings, pins, and auto spare parts, as well as cans, barrels, tins, and all kinds of packaging. The company was founded in 1967 and is headquartered in Izmit, Turkey. Federal-Mogul Izmit Piston Ve Pim Üretim Tesisleri A.S. operates as a subsidiary of Tenneco LLC.

stocks.name: Fonet Bilgi Teknolojileri A.S.
stocks.description: Fonet Bilgi Teknolojileri A.S. provides information technology services in the healthcare sector in Turkey and internationally. The company offers health informatics, digital health transformation, solutions social security, and family and social aid solutions such as healthcare software modules, including consultation management, appointment management, patient record/admission management, emergency management, polyclinic management, interoperability systems, decision support management, material resource and inventory management, fixture and asset management, home health care services management, and remote health information systems. The company also provides software development services, project implementation, and system support. In addition, it offers turnkey project services and develops, sells, and supports ERP products used in both public and private sectors. The company's products include Fonet Hospital Information Management System (HIS), that manages medical, administrative, and financial business processes of health institutions. Fonet Bilgi Teknolojileri A.S. was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Ankara, Turkey.

stocks.name: Formet Metal ve Cam Sanayi A.S.
stocks.description: Formet Metal ve Cam Sanayi A.S. engages in the manufacture and sale of steel doors primarily in Turkey. The company also provides steel, aluminum, wood, PVC, plastic, other materials; metal doors and windows, and their parts made of metal; and alloy and other materials, as well as door thresholds, shutters, stairs, banisters, verandas, railings, durable consumer goods, cookers, heaters, and electric appliances. It exports its products to Europe, Asia, America, Africa, and the Middle East. The company was formerly known as Formet Celik Kapi Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. and changed its name to Formet Metal ve Cam Sanayi A.S. in July 2021. Formet Metal ve Cam Sanayi A.S. was founded in 2005 and is based in Kayseri, Turkey.

stocks.name: Forte Bilgi Iletisim Teknolojileri ve Savunma Sanayi A.S.
stocks.description: Forte Bilgi Iletisim Teknolojileri ve Savunma Sanayi A.S., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the system integration and software development businesses in Turkey and internationally. It operates through Commercial Activities, Software Activities, Crowdfunding Activities, and Agricultural Activities. The company offers various software, such as factory production management systems, integrated logistics support systems, smart project portfolio management and analysis systems, interactive technical documentation system viewers and editors, unmanned aerial vehicle management information systems, Azerbaijan personnel and logistics management information systems, artificial intelligence assistants, and crowdfunding platform systems. It also provides field services, material coding, professional technical documentation authoring, IT service management, personnel outsourcing, professional installation, and strategic database consulting and data analysis services. In addition, the company offers business continuity, disaster recovery, and backup; CCTV systems; virtualization and consolidation solutions; data storage systems; server system solutions; infrastructure solutions; data center solutions; cyber security solutions; and enterprise network solutions. Further, it engages in electronic computing; purchase and sale of communication machines; production and development of operating system software and productivity enhancing software, as well as agricultural systems and technologies; and purchase, sale, and marketing of electronic information processing parts. The company serves the defense, IT, agriculture, finance, energy, and manufacturing industries; and public institutions. Forte Bilgi Iletisim Teknolojileri ve Savunma Sanayi A.S. was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in Ankara, Turkey.

stocks.name: Frigo-Pak Gida Maddeleri Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Frigo-Pak Gida Maddeleri Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. produces and sells frozen and canned fruit, vegetable juice, fruit juice, fruit and vegetable purees, and tomato pastes in Turkey. It offers mandarin, red grapefruit, apple, orange, cherry, mango, tomato, pineapple, pomegranate, and black grape juices under the Sunpride brand, as well as carbonated beverages, such as soft drinks, colas, and sodas. The company also provides frozen fruits and vegetables, including blackberry, raspberry, strawberry, sour cherry, black cherry, pomegranate, orange, grapefruit, mandarin, orange peel, plum, fig, pepper, and roasted eggplant; canned foods, such as mandarin, grapefruit, orange, black cherry, pomegranate, sour cherry, plum, and strawberry; and canned vegetables, such as red pepper, green pepper, artichokes, roasted red pepper, and red kidney beans. It also exports its products. Frigo-Pak Gida Maddeleri Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. was incorporated in 1984 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Fuzul Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi Anonim Sirketi

stocks.name: Garanti Faktoring A.S.
stocks.description: Garanti Faktoring A.S. provides factoring services to industrial and commercial firms. The company offers financing, cash flow management, guarantee, and collection services in selling goods/services; and supplier financing services in buying goods/services. It serves SMEs, and corporations through supplier and dealer networks in Turkey. The company was formerly known as Garanti Faktoring Hizmetleri A.S and changed its name to Garanti Faktoring A.S. in April 2014. Garanti Faktoring A.S. was incorporated in 1990 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. Garanti Faktoring A.S. is a subsidiary of Türkiye Garanti Bankasi A.S.

stocks.name: Gedik Yatirim Menkul Degerler A.S.
stocks.description: Gedik Yatirim Menkul Degerler A.S. provides investment banking company in Turkey and internationally. The company offers products such as, stock certificate, futures and options market, international market, investment funds, treasury transactions, public offering, and fixed income securities. It also provides brokerage services to investors in the equity market, repo/reverse repo market, debt securities market, international depository receipt market, international debt securities market, futures and options market, and leveraged trading transaction; individual services, such as portfolio management and investment consultancy services; and corporate services, including corporate finance, international corporate sales, public offering brokerage, and corporate treasury transaction services. The company was incorporated in 1991 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey. Gedik Yatirim Menkul Degerler A.S. operates as a subsidiary of Inveo Yatirim Holding Anonim Sirketi.

stocks.name: Gediz Ambalaj Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Gediz Ambalaj Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. produces and sells corrugated polypropylene (PP) sheets in Europe. It offers glass packaging, white goods and electronics, iron and steel, logistics, automotive, separators, stationery, boxes, multi-purpose boxes, archive boxes, recycling bins, vegetable and fruit boxes, flower boxes, cat dog kennel, signage and stands, beehive, construction and insulation, sapling protection, and greenhouse cover products. The company also engages in the intercity freight transportation and construction contracting works. Gediz Ambalaj Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. was founded in 1982 and is headquartered in Gediz, Turkey.

stocks.name: Gen Ilac Ve Saglik Urunleri Sanayi Ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Gen Ilac Ve Saglik Urunleri Sanayi Ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi, a pharmaceutical company, manufactures and supplies products to treat rare diseases and disorders worldwide. The company offers its products in various areas, such as neurology, endocrinology, nephrology, oncology, hematology, and pediatric. Gen Ilac Ve Saglik Urunleri Sanayi Ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi has collaboration with Sulfateq BV for the development of molecule SUL-238 as a treatment for Alzheimer's disease and other neurodegenerative diseases. In addition, it manufactures, trades, imports and exports of all kinds of human medicines and health products. The company was incorporated in 1997 and is headquartered in Çankaya, Turkey.

stocks.name: Gentas Dekoratif Yuzeyler Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Gentas Dekoratif Yuzeyler Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. engages in the production and sale of impregnated and laminate paper, table tops, school desks, chair, backrests, and building profiles in Turkey and internationally. The company was formerly known as Gentas Genel Metal Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. and changed its name to Gentas Dekoratif Yuzeyler Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. in April 2020. The company was incorporated in 1972 and is headquartered in Ankara, Turkey.

stocks.name: Gersan Elektrik Ticaret ve Sanayi Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Gersan Elektrik Ticaret ve Sanayi Anonim Sirketi, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the electrical materials and electrochemical contracting businesses in Turkey and internationally. The company offers power and lighting busbar systems; hot-dip galvanizing, pre-galvanized, stainless steel, and aluminum cable ducts and conveyor systems; standard cable channel and heavy-duty cable trays; and cable carriers, cable carrying systems, and cable ladder clamps. It also provides earth transition resistance value, current carrying capacity, and equipotential bond grounding systems; distribution panels, surface mounted distribution panels, rack cabinets, and solar panels; and underfloor and raised underfloor cable trays. In addition, the company offers electric vehicle charging stations; led-bus lighting systems; and g-bus automation systems, as well as after-sales services. It serves the power transmission line, defense, nuclear power plant, mechanical carrier system, building, industrial facility, factory, airport, oil and gas refinery, shopping mall, hotel, and hospital industries. The company sells its products under the 3M, Petrofac Qatar, Ensytec, ABB, Alstom, Mitsubishi Electric, Siemens, Thales, Kurgan-Balt, Cable Partners, Eurstrut, Anord, Depac, Arabian Falcon, Areva, Netzer, Centretech, Denge Energy Ltd, Hussian&Co, Nexans, Croon, MCS, Omega, RVC, Sea Star, Sidem, Petrofac, Polarvista, RS Group, Sun Expo Service, Alfaneyah, Caporal&Moretti, Eta-com, HP Busbars, Kaczmarek, Lokys, Power-Breeze, and Zao-Gersan-R brands. The company was formerly known as Gersan Ticaret. Gersan Elektrik Ticaret ve Sanayi Anonim Sirketi was founded in 1980 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Girisim Elektrik Sanayi Taahhüt ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Girisim Elektrik Sanayi Taahhüt ve Ticaret A.S. operates as an EPC contracting, engineering, sales, and marketing company. The company offers EPC and contracting services for HV and MV substations, electric distribution networks, transmission lines, and thermal, hydroelectrical, wind, solar, geothermal, biomass, and combined cycle natural gas power plants, cogeneration, railways and industrial facilities electrification, infrastructure, and power factor correction; urban and super structures; automation and SCADA projects. It also provides engineering services for project design and management, supervision, automation and SCADA, and testing and commissioning, as well as offers training services. In addition, the company markets and sells LV switch gear, LV-MV power factor correction reactors, automation SCADA equipment and data recorder, power protection and control equipment, LV panels, MV cells and switch gear facilities, and concrete and metallic kiosks metallic and package substations; mobile substation testing and measurement equipment, power and distribution transformers and accessories, and LV-MV-HV measurement and protection transformers, insulators, and cables and accessories; MV-HV circuit breakers, disconnectors, switching equipment, gas insulated switch gears, UPS, voltage regulators, MV-fuses, power transmission and distribution hardware, neutral earthing resistors, conductors, motor and drives, cable trays and busbar systems, LV-MV-HV surge arresters, and lightning and over-voltage protection equipment; grounding equipment, steel and concrete, power generation, and explosion-proof electrical and marine electrical products; lighting, electrical installation, health, safety, environment, railway catenary, and electrification equipment; and solar panels, mineral and natural transformer oils, inverters, solar and battery systems, and structures. Further, it provides testing services. The company was incorporated in 1999 and is based in Ankara, Turkey.

stocks.name: Gipta Ofis Kirtasiye ve Promosyon Ürünleri Imalat Sanayi A.S.
