In addition, the compantoffers paints and concrete chemicals. Further, the company provides port, storage, and warehousing services. Polisan Holding A.S. was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Politeknik Metal Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Politeknik Metal Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi manufactures and sells aluminum surface treatment chemicals in Türkiye. The company offers aluminum surface finishing chemicals, turnkey anodize lines, and equipment supply services, as well as engineering/design/consultancy services for anodizing lines. It also exports its products. The company was incorporated in 1985 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Türkiye. Politeknik Metal Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi is a subsidiary of Element Solutions Inc.

stocks.name: Pardus Girisim Sermayesi Yatirim Ortakligi Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Pardus Girisim Sermayesi Yatirim Ortakligi Anonim Sirketi operates as a corporate capital market company in Turkey. The company operates a portfolio of venture capital investments and capital market instruments, and other assets and transactions. It provides capital to businesses in industries such as communication services, food production, renewable energy, training and fleet leasing, and portfolio management. Pardus Girisim Sermayesi Yatirim Ortakligi Anonim Sirketi is based in ISTANBUL, Turkey.

stocks.name: Türk Prysmian Kablo ve Sistemleri Anonim Sirketi
stocks.address: Oemerbey Mah. Bursa Asfalti Cad. No:51
stocks.description: Türk Prysmian Kablo ve Sistemleri Anonim Sirketi produces, imports, exports, and trades in cables, conductors, machinery, apparatuses, tools and equipment, and spare parts and accessories worldwide. It offers energy cables, communication cables with copper conductors,railway signaling cables, studio broadcast cables, special cables and fiber optic cables; cable for utilities and power grids; telecom; transportation and mobility; and zero-carbon energy system. The company provides medium and low voltage, fire performance, and wire cables for trade and; cables for industries, including renewables, water treatment, and oil and gas. It offers its products under the Prysmian, and Draka brands. The company exports its products to approximately 50 countries. The company was formerly known as Turk Pirelli Kablo ve Sistemleri A.S. and changed its name to Türk Prysmian Kablo ve Sistemleri Anonim Sirketi in September 2005. The company was founded in 1964 and is headquartered in Mudanya, Turkey. Türk Prysmian Kablo ve Sistemleri Anonim Sirketi operates as a subsidiary of Draka Holding B.V.

stocks.name: Park Elektrik Üretim Madencilik Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Park Elektrik Üretim Madencilik Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S., through its subsidiary, Konya Ilgin Elektrik Üretim Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S., generates and sells electricity in Turkey. It focuses on establishing a thermal power plant with an installed capacity of 500MW in the Ilgin District, Konya. In addition, it is involved in exploration, extraction, processing, and operation of various minerals, ores, and their derivatives; textile business; and establishment of a thermal power plant with a 500MW installed capacity using fluidized bed boiler technology in Ilgin district, as well as sells generated electrical energy to wholesale and retail license holders and free consumers. The company was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. Park Elektrik Üretim Madencilik Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. is a subsidiary of Park Holding A.S.

stocks.name: Prizma Pres Matbaacilik Yayincilik Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Prizma Pres Matbaacilik Yayincilik Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. engages in the printing and publishing activities in Turkey. The company offers printing services for textbooks and supplementary textbooks, children's story and fairy tale books, and question banks and test books. It also engages in the purchasing and selling of paper; publishing and distribution of books, newspapers, and magazines; and importing and selling of printing machines. Prizma Pres Matbaacilik Yayincilik Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. was founded in 1975 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Pergamon Status Dis Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Pergamon Status Dis Ticaret A.S. operates as a mediate in the exports and imports of manufacturers in various industry. The company provides export intermediation services; and tax and foreign trade consultancy services related to tax, other financial legislations, customs, foreign exchange, export, import, inward processing, factoring, and Exim loans in foreign trade. It also offers legislation and bulletin services, such as changes and developments in tax and other financial legislation, and foreign trade legislation; contact meetings and panels; and information sharing services, such as information about the seminars, panels, or conferences. The company was formerly known as Pergamos Dis Ticaret A.S. and changed its name to Pergamon Status Dis Ticaret A.S. as a result of its merger with Status Dis Ticaret A.S. in 2005. Pergamon Status Dis Ticaret A.S. was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Izmir, Turkey.

stocks.name: Pasifik Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S.
stocks.description: Pasifik Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. focuses on operating as a REIT company in Turkey. It has various mixed projects. The company is based in Ankara, Turkey.

stocks.name: QUA Granite Hayal Yapi ve Ürünleri Sanayi Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: QUA Granite Hayal Yapi ve Ürünleri Sanayi Ticaret A.S. manufactures, exports, and sells ceramics, floor tiles, tile materials, and granite in Turkey, Europe, the United States, and internationally. The company also offers bathroom, kitchen, outdoor, and wall tiles. It sells its products through dealers, distributors, and construction market chains. QUA Granite Hayal Yapi ve Ürünleri Sanayi Ticaret A.S. was incorporated in 2015 and is based in Aydin, Turkey.

stocks.name: Ral Yatirim Holding A.S.
stocks.description: Ral Yatirim Holding A.S. engages in the construction, energy, and education activities. It carries contracting works for housing projects, as well as large public projects. The company is also involved in the production and sale of renewable and clean energy; and operation of Kyrenia college. Ral Yatirim Holding A.S. was founded in 1976 and is based in Ankara, Turkey.

stocks.name: Ray Sigorta Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Ray Sigorta Anonim Sirketi engages in the non-life insurance business in Turkey. The company offers accident, illness - health, land vehicles, aircraft, watercraft, transportation, fire, natural disasters, general damages, credit, financial losses, and legal protection insurance services; home insurance policies; and general liability insurance solutions. It sells its products through agencies, agency branches, brokers, broker branches, banks, and leasing companies. The company was incorporated in 1958 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. Ray Sigorta Anonim Sirketi operates as a subsidiary of ATBIH GmbH.

stocks.name: Reeder Teknoloji Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Reeder Teknoloji Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi produces and sells e-book readers, smart mobile phones and accessories, smart watches, and tablets in Turkey. The company also offers robot vacuum cleaners and smart televisions. Further, it manufactures and trades of computer peripherals and electric vehicles. In addition, it sells its products through online. The company was founded in 2010 and is based in Samsun, Turkey.

stocks.name: RONESANS GAYRIMENKUL YAT.
stocks.description: Ronesans Gayrimenkul Yatirim A.S., together with its subsidiaries, operates as the commercial real estate development and investment company in Türkiye. The company develops and manages shopping malls, office buildings, and other commercial real estate projects, as well as residential properties; It also provides management and consulting, and asset management services, as well as rents investment properties. The company was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Ankara, Türkiye. Ronesans Gayrimenkul Yatirim A.S. operates as a subsidiary of Ronesans Varlik ve Proje Yatirimlari A.S.

stocks.name: Rainbow Polikarbonat Sanayi Ticaret Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Rainbow Polikarbonat Sanayi Ticaret Anonim Sirketi provides polycarbonate, polymer, plastic, and related products. It offers polycarbonate roof panels, polycarbonate H and U shape products, rainbow 27/200 products, and polycarbonate hollow sheets. The company was incorporated in 1995 and is based in Kayseri, Türkiye.

stocks.name: Rodrigo Tekstil Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Rodrigo Tekstil Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. provides clothing products in Turkey. The company offers T-shirts, shirts, sweatshirts, trousers, jeans, tracksuits, jackets, and waistcoats for men. It provides its products through online, as well as stores. The company was formerly known as Rodrigo Tekstil Turizm Insaat Gida Ticaret ve Sanayi Anonim Sirketi and changed its name to Rodrigo Tekstil Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. in July 2012. Rodrigo Tekstil Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Royal Hali Iplik Tekstil Mobilya Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Royal Hali Iplik Tekstil Mobilya Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. manufactures and sells carpets in Turkey. The company was formerly known as Naksan Kimya Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. and changed its name to Royal Hali Iplik Tekstil Mobilya Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. in December 2007. The company was incorporated in 2000 and is based in Gaziantep, Turkey. Royal Hali Iplik Tekstil Mobilya Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. is a subsidiary of NAKSAN Holding.

stocks.name: RTA Laboratuvarlari Biyolojik Urunler Ilac ve Makine Sanayi Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: RTA Laboratuvarlari Biyolojik Urunler Ilac ve Makine Sanayi Ticaret A.S. engages in the research, development, and production of microbiology and molecular biology products in Turkey. It offers microbiology products, including petri dish, tube and bottle, chromogenic media, blood culture bottle, tuberculosis diagnostic, rapid test, microbiological stain, hygislide, surcheck media, membrane, painting sets, and swab products; and molecular biology products, such as nucleic acid isolation kits, real time PCR kits, and voltran viral load detection systems. RTA Laboratuvarlari Biyolojik Urunler Ilac ve Makine Sanayi Ticaret A.S. was incorporated in 1996 and is based in Kocaeli, Turkey.

stocks.name: Rubenis Tekstil Sanayi Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Rubenis Tekstil Sanayi Ticaret A.S. manufactures and sells cotton yarns and fabrics under Mayer brand in Turkey and internationally. It engages in the silk, cotton, wool, synthetic natural fibers, and other yarns knitting; dye and finish; construction; and air conditioning businesses. The company is also involved in the real estate development activities in the field of buildings, facilities, and landscape architecture; and manufacture, export, import, wholesale, and retail trade of textile fabrics. Rubenis Tekstil Sanayi Ticaret A.S. was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Sanliurfa, Turkey.

stocks.name: Reysas Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S.
stocks.description: Reysas Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. is a privately owned real estate investment trust.  It invests in the real estate markets of Turkey. The firm invests in the warehousing market. Reysas Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. is based in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Reysas Tasimacilik ve Lojistik Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Reysas Tasimacilik ve Lojistik Ticaret A.S. provides logistics solutions in Turkey and internationally. The company offers local transportation and distribution, automotive logistics, warehousing, railway transportation, international services, fuel logistics, and bonded warehousing. It also provides technology solutions, such as software services and vehicle tracking systems. In addition, the company distributes and markets tobacco products, and operates vehicle inspection station, as well as involved in the real estate investments. Reysas Tasimacilik ve Lojistik Ticaret A.S. was incorporated in 1989 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Safkar Ege Sogutmacilik Klima Soguk Hava Tesisleri Ihracat Ithalat Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Safkar Ege Sogutmacilik Klima Soguk Hava Tesisleri Ihracat Ithalat Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi produces and sells air conditioners. It offers commercial air conditioners for vehicles, such as minibuses, midi buses, and buses; refrigerated coolers; and metro, tram, light rail, and train air conditioners, as well as air conditioners for the defense industry and electric vehicles. The company also manufactures and sells air conditioning and cold air facilities for motorized road vehicles, rail systems, and marine transportation vehicles. The company was founded in 1988 and is headquartered in Izmir, Turkey.

stocks.name: Saray Matbaacilik Kagitçilik kirtasiyecilik Ticaret Ve Sanayi A.S.
stocks.description: Saray Matbaacilik Kagitçilik kirtasiyecilik Ticaret Ve Sanayi A.S. engages in the production and sale of stationery products in Turkey. The company provides paper products, including woodfree offset printing, coated, photocopy, and book papers; exercise books, such as PP cover, wire-o-spiral, single spiral, soft cover, spiral binding, stapled binding, glued binding, and hard cover notebooks; and calendars. It also provides a range of services comprising printing preparation, pre printing, and after printing, as well as paper sheeting services; and sheet-fed offset, web offset, and continuous form printing systems. In addition, it provides food packaging products comprising paper bag for pastries, simit, and pita bread; baklava, cake, and tart boxes; black sea pita bread, hamburger, and chip boxes; polyethylene-coated paper for paper plates and cups; metallized lid for aluminum food containers; and polyethylene butcher paper. The company offers its products and services under the Yildiz Yayincilik, Vizyon, Papicat, and SRY,BIL brands. It exports its products to England, Sweden, Hungary, Greece, and Israel. The company was founded in 1982 and is based in Ankara, Turkey.

stocks.name: San-el Mühendislik Elektrik Taahhüt Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: San-el Mühendislik Elektrik Taahhüt Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. designs, manufactures, and sells electrical panels in Turkey. It offers LV panel, LV harmonic filter, MV compensation and harmonic filter, SVC flicker compensation, and weak current systems, as well as OG metal clad cells. The company engages in distribution of control panels related activities. San-el Mühendislik Elektrik Taahhüt Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. was founded in 2005 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Sanifoam Endustri ve Tuketim Urunleri Sanayi Ticaret A.S.
stocks.address: Gazi Osman Pasa OSB Mah. 21. Sk. No: 6/A
stocks.description: Sanifoam Endustri ve Tuketim Urunleri Sanayi Ticaret A.S., together with its subsidiaries, produces and trades in industrial and cleaning products in Turkey and internationally. The company offers Basotect and Firex foams; Echobon, a high-density ecological insulation material; Echopol, a low-density flexible foam product; SaniFilter material; SaniShine, a high strength flexible polyurethane foam; SaniHydro sponge, which comprises Hydro-F31, Hydro-M35, and Hydro-G; SaniFelt, a fibre felt products; SaniSeal, a sealing material; SaniTape, a self-adhesive tape; coating and layering products; and SaniWood, a plywood and compact laminate products. It also provides scrubber sponges, cleaning clothes, bath sponges, and scouring fibers, as well as car sponges with shampoo under the Sanitex, Star, and Blues brands; microfiber clothes, stainless steel scourers, and melamine and cellulosic sponges; and polyether and polyester sponge. In addition, the company offers logistics services, which include storage and distribution services. It serves the automotive, home appliances, industrial insulation, acoustics, and cleaning sectors. Sanifoam Endustri ve Tuketim Urunleri Sanayi Ticaret A.S. was founded in 1990 and is headquartered in Tekirdag, Turkey.

stocks.name: Sanko Pazarlama Ithalat Ihracat Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Sanko Pazarlama Ithalat Ihracat Anonim Sirketi develops, purchases, imports, exports, markets, and sells dyed and non-dyed yarns, and artificial and synthetic fibers in Turkey and internationally. The company offers hydrophilic cotton weaving, knitting, and clothing of industrial goods and other textile products. It also provides ring carded and combed, melange, slub, core spun, dyed, core twist, and organic cotton yarns; and knitted fabrics, such as single jersey, rib, interlock, two and three thread fleece, terry and towel, and pique fabrics, as well as knitted fabrics with elasthane. In addition, the company offers woven fabrics, including stretch, novelty, and overdyed denim fabrics; sportswear; cotton woven fabrics; cot-stretch fabrics; color woven products; and curduroy fabrics, as well as printed fabrics. The company was formerly known as Temko Pazarlama Sanayi ve Ticaret Anonim Sirketi and changed its name to Sanko Pazarlama Ithalat Ihracat Anonim Sirketi in March 1998. Sanko Pazarlama Ithalat Ihracat Anonim Sirketi was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Sarkuysan Elektrolitik Bakir Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Sarkuysan Elektrolitik Bakir Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S., together with its subsidiaries, produces and trades in electrolytic copper wires, copper pipes, coppering, and copper alloys in Turkey. It offers electrolytic copper cathode products; oxygen free and ETP wire rods; DHP and ETP copper billets; bare, tin plated, and nickel plated copper single wires; bare and tin plated, and nickel plated multi wires, as well as bare and tin plated multi wires on braider bobbins; and bare, tin plated, and nickel plated bunched conductors. The company also provides flat wires and profiles, and PV ribbon wires; copper and copper alloy contact wires, and stranded copper and copper alloy conductors; copper tubes and busbars; and copper nuggets. In addition, it offers electrolytic copper conductors; packaging materials and machinery; and hermetic compressor parts, scroll compressor parts, nodular and gray iron parts, brake and vented brake discs, hub drums, flywheels, exhaust manifolds, rings, brake cylinders, and brackets and brake security parts. Further, the company is involved in marketing and distribution and real estate rental activities. Its products are used in various industries, including electro technique, electronic, motor, communication, power generation and distribution, solar and renewable energy, home appliances, measurement instruments, defense, automotive, chemical, construction, heating ventilation, air-conditioning, and sanitary plumbing. The company also exports its products to approximately 80 countries worldwide. The company was incorporated in 1972 and is headquartered in Darica, Turkey.

stocks.name: Say Yenilenebilir Enerji Ekipmanlari Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Say Yenilenebilir Enerji Ekipmanlari Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. offers renewable energy equipment in Turkey. The company produces parts made of steel, aluminum, and other materials for electricity generation; integral parts, such as inner and outer parts of wind turbine towers and generators; and wind turbine and wind turbine transportation equipment. It also engages in trade, marketing, and sales activities; industrial advertising; buildings and outdoor design; production and assembly of all visual communication products; interior and exterior furniture and decoration works; steel and reinforced concrete structure manufacturing, purchase and sale; and project contracting and exterior industrial coating works. The company was formerly known as Say Reklamcilik Yapi Dekorasyon Proje Taahhüt Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. and changed its name to Say Yenilenebilir Enerji Ekipmanlari Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. in October 2020. Say Yenilenebilir Enerji Ekipmanlari Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. was founded in 1989 and is headquartered in Izmir, Turkey.

stocks.name: SDT Uzay ve Savunma Teknolojileri Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: SDT Uzay ve Savunma Teknolojileri Anonim Sirketi engages in the production and sale of defense electronics and software products in Turkey and internationally. The company offers radar, electronic warfare, and communication systems; mission systems comprising platform management, data recording, and launcher management systems; and production program that include RF jammer systems, guidance electronics, and integrated systems solutions. It also provides simulation systems and information technologies, such as air combat training, land combat, naval combat, and satellite and UAV systems, as well as image processing and data technologies, geographic information system-based digital twin and asset management technologies, and cloud-based autonomous data processing technologies. The company was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in Ankara, Turkey.

stocks.name: SEGMEN KARDESLER GIDA
stocks.description: Segmen Kardesler Gida Üretim ve Ambalaj Sanayi Anonim Sirketi produces and sells food products in Turkey. The company offers jam, diabetic and sugar-free jam, probiotic jam, honey, halva, diabetic halva, peanut butter, tahini, grape molasses, tahini molasses, Turkish delight, spices, herbal tea, and butter. It also sells its products through online. The company was founded in 1938 and is headquartered in Ankara, Turkey.

stocks.name: Seker Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S.
stocks.description: Seker Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. is based in Istanbul, Turkey. Seker Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. operates as a subsidiary of Sekerbank T.A.S.

stocks.name: Seker Finansal Kiralama A.S.
stocks.description: Seker Finansal Kiralama A.S. provides equipment financing and leasing services. It offers leasing services for the purchase of production machinery, construction equipment and forklifts, logistics transportation and transportation equipment, commercial/passenger vehicles, agriculture equipment, medical devices, yachts and boats, real estate, and energy production and technology packages, as well as real estate comprising business premises, offices, factory buildings, lands, etc. The company also provides operational leasing, SME, women entrepreneurs, start-up, and sales lease back packages; and insurance services. Seker Finansal Kiralama A.S. was incorporated in 1997 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Sekuro Plastik Ambalaj Sanayi A.S.
stocks.description: Sekuro Plastik Ambalaj Sanayi A.S. engages in the manufacture and sale of plastic packaging products in Turkey. The company offers PE air bubble films, such as standard bubble films, opaque protection products, and insulation products. It also provides PE shrink films; PE general packaging films; bag and sheet products; and technical films. The company was incorporated in 1997 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Selçuk Ecza Deposu Ticaret ve Sanayi A.S.
stocks.description: Selçuk Ecza Deposu Ticaret ve Sanayi A.S., together with its subsidiary, operates as a pharmacy depot primarily in Turkey. It also organizes distribution channels between drug manufacturers, hospitals, and pharmacies. In addition, the company is involved in operation of pharmaceutical warehouses; and distributes cosmetics, personal care, infant food, vitamins, medical, and other products. The company was founded in 1958 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. Selçuk Ecza Deposu Ticaret ve Sanayi A.S. is a subsidiary of Selçuk Ecza Holding A.S.

stocks.name: Selva Gida Sanayi A.S.
stocks.description: Selva Gida Sanayi A.S. manufactures and sells various food products in Turkey. It offers various types of pasta, such as penne rigate, farfalle, sedanini, fusilli, elbow, elbow rigate, ditalini, farfalle tonde, ditaloni, pipe rigate, tagliatelle, bucatini, linguine, spaghetti, vermicelli, risoni, and filini; as well as wheat flour and semolina. The company also provides dessert and salad products. In addition, it is involved in the catering business. The company was incorporated in 1988 and is headquartered in Konya, Turkey.

stocks.name: Seyitler Kimya Sanayi A.S.
stocks.description: Seyitler Kimya Sanayi A.S. develops and sells medical adhesive tape products in Turkey. The company offers health medical plasters, first aid patches, wound dressings, dialysis kits, eye pads, capsicum, and rheumatism plasters used in health institutions. It also provides surgical tapes, first aid strips, band-aid, biocidal products, disposable surgical products, injection series, and wound care products. The company exports its products worldwide. It serves government, private hospitals, medical wholesalers, and pharmacies. Seyitler Kimya Sanayi A.S. was incorporated in 1991 and is headquartered in Turgutlu, Turkey.

stocks.name: Silverline Endustri ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Silverline Endustri ve Ticaret A.S. produces and sells aspirators, hoods, ovens, built-in hobs, built-in dishwashers, washing machines, and refrigerators. It also produces a range of accessories, such as external motors, stovetop, and curved and standard remote controls. The company was formerly known as Gumusfon Metal Endustri ve Ticaret A.S. and changed its name to Silverline Endustri ve Ticaret A.S. in 2005. Silverline Endustri ve Ticaret A.S. was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Söktas Tekstil Sanayi Ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Söktas Tekstil Sanayi Ve Ticaret A.S., through its subsidiaries, engages in the textile and dairy farming businesses in Turkey and internationally. The company produces and sells raw and finished fabrics. It is also involved in the dairy cow breeding, milk production, and raw milk sales activities; yarn and fabric trade; and transfer and spinning of cotton and fiber yarns. The company was incorporated in 1971 and is headquartered in Aydin, Turkey.

stocks.name: Skyalp Finansal Teknolojiler ve Danismanlik A.S.
stocks.description: Skyalp Finansal Teknolojiler ve Danismanlik A.S. an investment company, engages in the incubation and investment in financial technology companies in Turkey. It operates Napolyon, personal banking platform. The company was formerly known as Ideal Finansal Teknolojiler ve Danismanlik Anonim Sirketi and changed its name to Skyalp Finansal Teknolojiler ve Danismanlik A.S. in February 2024. Skyalp Finansal Teknolojiler ve Danismanlik A.S. was incorporated in 1998 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: SEKER YATIRIM
stocks.description: Seker Yatirim Menkul Degerler A.S. provides capital market services in Turkey. It offers equity trading, SWEET, fixed income trading, corporate financing, research, asset management, investment advisory services, derivatives trading, and FX trading; and brokerage, portfolio brokerage, private portfolio management, investment advisory, initial public offering, and custody services. The company was incorporated in 1996 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey. Seker Yatirim Menkul Degerler A.S. is a subsidiary of Sekerbank T.A.S.

stocks.name: Smartiks Yazilim A.S.
stocks.description: Smartiks Yazilim A.S. provides business solutions, software development, and consultancy services in Türkiye. It offers data security, outsourcing, analysis and process management, data science, data warehouse, customer relationship management, human resources, and software development services. The company was founded in 2006 and is based in Istanbul, Türkiye.

stocks.name: Smart Günes Enerjisi Teknolojileri Arastirma ve Gelistirme Üretim Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Smart Günes Enerjisi Teknolojileri Arastirma ve Gelistirme Üretim Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S., an integrated solar technology company, produces solar photovoltaic modules in Turkey. The company also installs renewable energy plants; and provides engineering and labor services. In addition, it engages in selling and marketing various solar power plant system equipment. Further, the company is involved in the research and development activities for the electrical energy sector, including power grids and power generation facilities; provides maintenance and operation services of technical infrastructure and systems; manages turnkey projects for the electrical energy sector; offers project installation and maintenance repairs of low voltage lines and facilities, electrical networks, transformers, electricity distribution panels and tables, control systems, and meters. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. Smart Günes Enerjisi Teknolojileri Arastirma ve Gelistirme Üretim Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. is a subsidiary of Smart Holding A.S.

stocks.name: Sinpas Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S.
stocks.description: Sinpas Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S., formerly Sinpas Insaat, is a Turkish real estate investment trust (REIT) established in 2006 and transformed into a REIT in 2007. It focuses on developing residential and sales real estate projects and operates under the Sinpas Group Companies. In 2018, Sinpas GYO merged with Sinpas Yapi to enhance operational and economic synergies. Following the merger, the company's capital increased to 873.2 million TL. As of March 2025, the Group employs 188 people and is headquartered in Besiktas, Istanbul.

stocks.name: Sanica Isi Sanayi A.S.
stocks.description: Sanica Isi Sanayi A.S. produces and sells radiators, towel warmers, boilers, built-in reservoirs, control panels, and underground and aboveground pipes in Türkiye. The company offers condensing and combi boilers; standard and design panel radiators; aluminum, column, stainless steel, and steel design radiators; and standard and dizayn towel rails, as well as accessories. It offers its products under the Sanica brand. The company was incorporated in 1982 and is based in Istanbul, Türkiye.

stocks.name: Senkron Siber Güvenlik Yazilim ve Bilisim Cözümleri A.S.
stocks.description: Senkron Siber Güvenlik Yazilim ve Bilisim Cözümleri A.S. imports, exports, and installs security, communication, and computer systems in Turkey and internationally. The company offers software and information solutions development, closed circuit television systems, video management software, access control systems, intrusion alarm systems, fire detection systems, emergency exit and fire escape direction units, fire extinguishing systems, perimeter security systems, video intercom systems, parking lot safety barriers, road blockers, and high-speed doors. The company also provides license plate recognition, RFID, fast toll collection, under-vehicle surveillance systems, metal gate and hand detectors, X-ray control devices, explosive and narcotic detection systems, turnstile and full-length high security cabinets, public address and voice evacuation systems, electronic article surveillance systems, and artworks wireless security systems. In addition, it offers telepresence systems, guard tour control systems, bullet-proof glass and safety window films, security token and asset management systems, and building automation systems. It serves banking and finance, and private and public institutions, as well as retail and chain stores and residential and living areas. The company was incorporated in 1997 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Sönmez Pamuklu Sanayii A.S.
stocks.description: Sönmez Pamuklu Sanayii A.S. engages in the manufacturing, dyeing, and sale of various yarns and fibers in Turkey. It produces viscose, tencel, modal, micromodal, microtencel, acrylic, wool, silk, linen, elastane, bamboo, and polyester fibers. The company is also involved in real estate leasing activities. Sönmez Pamuklu Sanayii A.S. was founded in 1981 and is based in Bursa, Turkey.

stocks.name: Sodas Sodyum Sanayii A.S.
stocks.description: Sodas Sodyum Sanayii A.S. produces and sells chemicals in Turkey. The company offers natural sodium sulphate for use in the production of detergent, textile dyeing, glass, paper, fertilizer, animal feed, and various chemicals. It also provides sodium chloride (salt) for the food, textile, leather, detergent, animal feed, and health sectors, as well as against icing on highways in winter. Sodas Sodyum Sanayii A.S. was incorporated in 1974 and is headquartered in Izmir, Turkey.

stocks.name: Sönmez Filament Sentetik Iplik ve Elyaf Sanayi A.S.
stocks.description: Sönmez Filament Sentetik Iplik ve Elyaf Sanayi A.S. manufactures and sells yarns and fibers in Turkey. The company offers poy, flat yarn, textured yarn, twisted yarn, and dyed yarn suitable, as well as high-filament yarn and various types of fibers for the automotive industry. It is also involved in leasing of real estates. The company was incorporated in 1972 and is headquartered in Bursa, Turkey.

stocks.name: Servet Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S.
stocks.description: Servet Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. is a real estate investment trust. Servet Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. is based in Instanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Sumas Suni Tahta ve Mobilya Sanayi A.S.
stocks.description: Sumas Suni Tahta ve Mobilya Sanayi A.S. produces and sells oriented strand board panels and glue products in Turkey. It also provides natural fuel pellets. Its products are used in various applications, including roof covering, shingle plate, floorings, and combined and single applications; vehicle body manufacturing; interior decoration and packaging applications; construction and decoration of shops, and interior parts of barracks and prefabricated buildings; construction of warehouses, stages, gyms, schools, rows, and tables; construction of moisture proof, flat, and insulated surfaces; structural floors, walls, and partition structures; and wall coverings and under sidings. Sumas Suni Tahta ve Mobilya Sanayi A.S. was incorporated in 1976 and is headquartered in Balikesir, Turkey.

stocks.name: Sun Tekstil Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.address: Yedi Eylül Mah. Celal Umur Cad.
stocks.description: Sun Tekstil Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. designs, produces, and sells women's clothing collections for brands in Turkey. The company offers knit fabrics and ready-made womenswear garments. It also exports its products. The company was founded in 1987 and is headquartered in Izmir, Turkey.

stocks.name: Suwen Tekstil Sanayi Pazarlama A.S.
stocks.description: Suwen Tekstil Sanayi Pazarlama A.S. produces and sells underwear, home wear, corsets, and beach wear in Turkey. It provides bra, briefs, pajamas, nighty, dressing gowns, shorts pajamas, garter, bodysuits, pregnant/postpartum products, and socks for women. The company sells its products in retail stores with its own brand, and on its own e-commerce website. The company was formerly known as Ekofer Tesktil Parfümeri Sanayi Pazarlama Limited Sirketi and changed its name to Suwen Tekstil Sanayi Pazarlama A.S. in July 2018. Suwen Tekstil Sanayi Pazarlama A.S. was founded in 2003 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Tarkim Bitki Koruma Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Tarkim Bitki Koruma Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. produces, sells, and markets plant protection products. The company was incorporated in 2009 and is based in Manisa, Türkiye.

stocks.name: Tatlipinar Enerji Uretim A.S.
stocks.description: Tatlipinar Enerji Uretim A.S. engages in the renewable energy generation business in Turkey. It engages in the establishing and commissioning of facilities for producing renewable energy; electricity production facilities; solar, wind, hydroelectric and all kinds of renewable energy systems; and selling produced electrical energy. The company was founded in 2011 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Tat Gida Sanayi A.S.
stocks.description: Tat Gida Sanayi A.S., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the production and sale of tomato and canned products in Turkey and internationally. Its products include tomato pastes, sauces, convenience food, and pickles. It also offers food, beverages, agricultural, and animal foodstuffs and products; and frozen, dried, and powdered raw materials, including processed varieties, and auxiliary and additives, as well as engages in the production, distribution, and marketing of domestic and semi-finished products of sugar-free juice. Tat Gida Sanayi A.S. was formerly known as Tat Konserve Sanayii AS. and changed its name to Tat Gida Sanayi A.S. in November 2013. Tat Gida Sanayi A.S. was incorporated in 1967 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Türk Tuborg Bira ve Malt Sanayii A.S.
stocks.description: Türk Tuborg Bira ve Malt Sanayii A.S. produces, sells, and distributes beer and malt in Turkey and internationally. The company offers its products under the Tuborg, Carlsberg, FREDERIK, Troy, and 1664 Blanc brands, as well as imports GUINNESS, Weihenstephan, KILKENNY, Grimbergen, DESPERADOS, CAMPARI, APEROL, CINZANO, and SOL brands. It also exports its products to various countries, such as the United Kingdom, the Turkish Republic of Northern Cyprus, and Iraq. The company was incorporated in 1967 and is based in Izmir, Turkey. Türk Tuborg Bira ve Malt Sanayii A.S. is a subsidiary of International Beer Breweries Ltd.

stocks.name: Trend Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S.
stocks.description: Trend Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. engages in the real estate business in Turkey. It develops and constructs various real estate projects, such as houses, hotels, residence, and university buildings. The company was formerly known as Anda Gayrimenkul Gelistirme ve Insaat Sanayi Ticaret Limited Sirketi and changed its name to Trend Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. in November 2017. Trend Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. was founded in 2006 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Tek-Art Insaat Ticaret Turizm Sanayi ve Yatirimlar Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Tek-Art Insaat Ticaret Turizm Sanayi ve Yatirimlar Anonim Sirketi engages in the tourism business in Turkey and internationally. It invests, builds, and operates hotels, holiday villages, resorts, golf facilities, restaurants, cafeterias, casinos and entertainment venues, beaches, amusement parks, marinas, yacht docks, tourist goods outlets, and regulation schools and related facilities. The company conducts hotel management activities at the Zigana Hotel resort. In addition, it offers tourism transportation and rental car operations, as well as acts as a travel agent. Further, the company operates stores, display areas, and warehouses in ports and free zones. Tek-Art Insaat Ticaret Turizm Sanayi ve Yatirimlar Anonim Sirketi was founded in 1987 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Tera Yatirim Menkul Degerler A.S.
stocks.description: Tera Yatirim Menkul Degerler A.S. engages in investment banking and brokerage activities in Turkey. The company offers institutional sales and trading services for mutual funds, hedge funds, and alpha capture funds investors; private sales and trading services, as well as personalized financial advisory services, stocks, bonds, and funds; and investment banking services, such as initial public offering underwriting, debt instrument issuance facilitation, capital increase support, company valuation, financing options, and merger and acquisition consultancy. It is also involved in facilitating share purchase offers, exit rights, rights to withdraw from partnership/sell; and managing the process of wholesale market transactions and the process of sales to corporate/qualified investors. The company was incorporated in 1990 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Europap Tezol Kagit Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Europap Tezol Kagit Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. produces and sells cleaning papers and reel paper materials in Turkey. It offers jumbo rolls, napkins, dispenser towel, toilet papers, and kitchen towels under the Softy, Mare, Ecco Y.D, and Dolce brands as well as private label brands. The company was incorporated in 1969 and is based in Izmir, Turkey.

stocks.name: TGS Dis Ticaret Anonim Sirketi
stocks.address: Büyükdere Cad. Özsezen Is Merkezi D
stocks.description: TGS Dis Ticaret Anonim Sirketi provides intermediary services to exporters companies in Turkey. Its primary business is to mediate the export activities of the manufacturers and to collect the value added tax refunds on behalf of its customers due to their export transactions in the textile, mining, and other sectors. The company was incorporated in 1999 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Tekfen Holding Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Tekfen Holding Anonim Sirketi, together with its subsidiaries, engages in engineering and contracting, agriculture, and investment businesses in Turkey, CIS, the Middle Eastern countries, and internationally. It operates through three segments: Engineering and Contracting, Agricultural Industry, and Investment. The company provides turnkey solutions for various facilities, such as pipelines, oil and gas terminals, tank farms, oil refineries, offshore oil rigs, pump and compressor stations, power plants, industrial plants, petrochemical plants, highway and metro projects, sports complexes, steel structures, and superstructure and infrastructure projects. It also undertakes the production of agricultural inputs, including seeds and saplings; and produces bread and durum wheat seeds, table and seed potatoes, banana fruits, and banana saplings. In addition, the company engages in the terminal management; ship agency business; free zone management; insurance; development, leasing, operation, and management of properties; facility management services, including general maintenance, repair, cleaning, and security services, as well as management of spaces, such as parking facilities, conference halls, restaurants, and fitness centers; management services; trading of fertilizers; manufacture of fruits; trading activities; and energy business. Tekfen Holding Anonim Sirketi was founded in 1956 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Teknosa Iç ve Dis Ticaret Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Teknosa Iç ve Dis Ticaret Anonim Sirketi engages in the retail sale of technology products in Turkey. The company sells its products through its stores; air conditioners and refrigerators through its dealer network; and solar energy systems. The company also provides e-commerce services, including marketplace operations, and derives rental income from investment properties. The company was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. Teknosa Iç ve Dis Ticaret Anonim Sirketi operates as a subsidiary of Haci Ömer Sabanci Holding A.S.

stocks.name: Trabzon Liman Isletmeciligi Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Trabzon Liman Isletmeciligi Anonim Sirketi operates the Port of Trabzon. The port connects Iran, Iraq, Russia, and the Turkic Republics to all European and international markets. The company provides pilotage, towage, harboring, shifting, mooring, loading, unloading, terminal, warehousing, and passenger lounge management. It also provides water and electricity to ships; and receiving waste from ships. The company was incorporated in 2003 and is based in Trabzon, Turkey.

stocks.name: Temapol Polimer Plastik ve Insaat Sanayi Ticaret Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Temapol Polimer Plastik ve Insaat Sanayi Ticaret Anonim Sirketi manufactures and sells thermoplastic sheets in Turkey and internationally. It sells its products to the furniture, bath and shower, automotive and vehicle, medical, advertising goods, temaglass, high gloss acrylic, ABS-acrylic sheets, HIPS sheets, glass products, and white goods and cooling industries. It also provides packaging solutions and printing services. The company serves customers in the medical, furniture, textile, and construction sectors. The company was incorporated in 2007 and is based in Kayseri, Turkey.

stocks.name: Turcas Petrol A.S.
stocks.description: Turcas Petrol A.S. operates as a petrol and energy-focused investment company in Turkey. It operates through Petrol and Electricity segments. The company's products include fuel, lubricants, and engine oil. It is also involved in the power generation activities. The company was founded in 1931 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. Turcas Petrol A.S. operates as a subsidiary of Aksoy Girisimcilik Enerji Ve Turizm A.S.

stocks.name: Torunlar Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S.
stocks.description: Torunlar Real Estate Investment Partnership Inc. (Torunlar GYO or Company). The Company was established in Istanbul, Türkiye, in 1996 under the name Toray Construction Industry and Trade Inc. The Company with the amendment to the articles of association published in the Trade Registry Gazette on January 25, 2008, it was registered as Torunlar Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. on January 21, 2008. The Company is registered with the Capital Markets Board ("CMB") and its shares have been traded on Borsa Istanbul since October 21, 2010. The Company operates in Türkiye. As of June 30, 2025, the Company had 55 employees (December 31, 2024: 56), and the ultimate parent company is the Torun Family. The company is registered with the Istanbul Chamber of Commerce in Türkiye and its headquarters is located at the following address: Rüzgarlibahçe Mahallesi Özalp Çikmazi No: 4 Beykoz 34805 Istanbul/Türkiye. The Company's main field of activity is to engage in real estate, real estate-based capital market instruments, real estate projects and investments in capital market instruments, as outlined in the CMB's regulations on real estate investment trusts.

stocks.name: Turk Ilac Ve Serum Sanayi Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Turk Ilac Ve Serum Sanayi Anonim Sirketi produces and sells human tablets, parenteral solutions, nutritional solutions, amino acids, and other chemicals in Turkey. It also offers bulb, biological, and serum products, as well as medical devices. The company was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Ankara, Turkey.

stocks.name: TSKB Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S
stocks.description: TSKB Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S invests in real estate projects, capital market instruments backed by real estate, real estate development projects, and other capital market instruments. Its real estate development projects include shopping centers, hotels, office buildings, and others. The company was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Beyoglu, Turkey.

stocks.name: Türkiye Sinai Kalkinma Bankasi A.S.
stocks.description: Türkiye Sinai Kalkinma Bankasi A.S. operates as a development and investment bank in Turkey. The company offers corporate loans for renewable energy, industrial investments, energy and resource efficiency, women's employment and equal opportunity, environmental investments, investments in developing regions, research and development and innovation, occupational health and safety, education and health investments, and working capital financing. It also provides project finance for energy generation and power plants, including hydroelectric, geothermal, wind, solar, biomass, and combined cycle natural gas plants; electricity and natural gas distribution projects; mergers and acquisitions; logistics, transportation, and telecommunications; and public - private partnership projects. In addition, the company offers other loan products, such as wholesale banking loans, foreign trade finance, and financial leasing; letter of guarantees/external guarantees/letter of credits; and export/Eximbank endorsement, and country loans. Further, the company provides corporate finance products and services consisting of public offering preparation and brokerage, debt instrument issues, and mergers and acquisitions advisory; derivatives products comprising forward contracts, options, caps and floors, swap transactions, and swaptions; currency exchange, repo, warrant, and foreign derivative transactions; securities loans; brokerage for stock and bonds trading; and portfolio management and investment consulting services. Additionally, it provides financial planning and strategy, feasibility, valuation, and restructuring services, as well as sectoral analysis studies; and technical advisory, real estate appraisal, economic research, and sustainability consultancy services. Türkiye Sinai Kalkinma Bankasi A.S. was incorporated in 1950 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Trabzonspor Sportif Yatirim ve Futbol Isletmeciligi Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Trabzonspor Sportif Yatirim ve Futbol Isletmeciligi Ticaret A.S. operates Trabzonspor professional football team in Turkey. It also engages in activities related to its sports teams, including broadcasting and sponsorship contracts, and advertising contracts. The company was formerly known as Trabzonspor Sportif Yatirim ve Ticaret A.S. and changed its name to Trabzonspor Sportif Yatirim ve Futbol Isletmeciligi Ticaret A.S. in May 2011. The company was incorporated in 1994 and is based in Trabzon, Turkey. Trabzonspor Sportif Yatirim ve Futbol Isletmeciligi Ticaret A.S. is a subsidiary of Trabzonspor Futbol Isletmeciligi Ticaret A.S.

stocks.name: Tugçelik Alüminyum Ve Metal Mamulleri Sanayi Ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.address: Emek Mah Nato Yolu No: 282 Sancaktepe
stocks.description: Tugçelik Alüminyum Ve Metal Mamulleri Sanayi Ve Ticaret A.S. produces and sells pressure die casting aluminum parts in Turkey. It also engages in the melting, foundry, molding shop, CNC machining, and other processes activities. It serves automotive, white goods, telecommunication, agricultural equipment, electrical, and mechanical industries. Tugçelik Alüminyum Ve Metal Mamulleri Sanayi Ve Ticaret A.S. was founded in 1988 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Tukas Gida Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Tukas Gida Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the manufacture and sale of food products in Turkey and internationally. It offers tomato and pepper pastes, dried and grated tomatoes, sauces, spreads, and condiments; roasted and canned products; boiled products; and pickles, ready to serve foods, jams, and olives, as well as catering products. The company sells its products under the Tukas brand name. It also engages in the field of import, export, food trade, logistics works, construction works, transportation, and marketing business. Tukas Gida Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. was founded in 1962 and is headquartered in Izmir, Turkey.

stocks.name: Tureks Turizm Tasimacilik Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Tureks Turizm Tasimacilik Anonim Sirketi engages in group transportation, and fleet and individual car rental activities in Turkey. It is involved in the urban, suburban and rural areas, highways, personnel, students, and group transportation, as well as fleet and individual vehicle rental. The company was incorporated in 2002 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Türker Proje Gayrimenkul ve Yatirim Gelistirme A.S.
stocks.description: Türker Proje Gayrimenkul ve Yatirim Gelistirme A.S., owns and develops real estate properties in Turkey. The company was formerly known as Mutlu Yatirim Proje ve Gayrimenkul Gelistirme A.S. and changed its name to Türker Proje Gayrimenkul ve Yatirim Gelistirme A.S. in May 2015. The company was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. Türker Proje Gayrimenkul ve Yatirim Gelistirme A.S. is a subsidiary of Türker Yatirim Holding A.S.

stocks.name: Türkiye Sigorta A.S.
stocks.description: Türkiye Sigorta A.S. operates as a non-life insurance company in Turkey. It offers auto and non-auto accident, fire, transportation, engineering, health, agriculture, liability, financial losses, credit, and legal protection insurance products. Türkiye Sigorta A.S. was formerly known as Günes Sigorta Anonim Sirketi and changed its name to Türkiye Sigorta A.S. in August 2020. The company was incorporated in 1957 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey. Türkiye Sigorta A.S. operates as a subsidiary of TVF Finansal Yatirimlar AS.

stocks.name: UFUK Yatirim Yonetim ve Gayrimenkul A.S.
stocks.description: UFUK Yatirim Yonetim ve Gayrimenkul A.S. engages in financial leasing business in Turkey. It land and building. It also offers business management and consultancy services. The company was formerly known as Fon Sinai Yatirimlar A.S. and changed its name to UFUK Yatirim Yonetim ve Gayrimenkul A.S. in May 2016. UFUK Yatirim Yonetim ve Gayrimenkul A.S. was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. UFUK Yatirim Yonetim ve Gayrimenkul A.S. operates as a subsidiary of Yildiz Holding A.S.

stocks.name: Ulusal Faktoring A.S.
stocks.description: Ulusal Faktoring A.S. provides factoring services in Turkey. The company was incorporated in 1999 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Ulusoy Elektrik Imalat Taahhüt ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.address: 1. Organize Sanayi Bölgesi Oguz Cad. No:6
stocks.description: Ulusoy Elektrik Imalat Taahhüt ve Ticaret A.S. manufactures and sells electrical equipment for medium voltage power distribution networks and industrial plants in Turkey. It offers metal enclosed modular, metal clad, and gas insulated switchgears; and compact transformer substations, medium voltage distribution transformers and switchgear components, and medium voltage cable accessories. The company was incorporated in 1985 and is headquartered in Ankara, Turkey. Ulusoy Elektrik Imalat Taahhüt ve Ticaret A.S. operates as a subsidiary of Eaton Industries XX Unlimited Company.

stocks.name: Ulusoy Un Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S.
stocks.description: Ulusoy Un Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. produces and sells flour in Turkey. It operates through Production and Trade in Agricultural Commodities and Licensed Warehousing segments. The company offers baguette, sugar bread-toast bread, croissant, pastry, chapati, noodle, biscuit, all purpose flour, industrial wheat flour, pizza, and Arabic bread. It also engages in warehousing activities for the storage of agricultural products; production, wholesale, retail purchase, sale, distribution, import, and export of food products; manufacture, purchase, sale, import, and export of warehousing activities for the storage of agricultural products; buying and selling of real estate; and production, distribution, and trading of pasta. The company provides its products under the U Plus, U Pro, and U Chef brand names. It also exports its products. Ulusoy Un Sanayi ve Ticaret A.S. was founded in 1969 and is headquartered in Samsun, Turkey.

stocks.name: Umpas Holding A.S.
stocks.description: Umpas Holding A.S. engages in the production and sell of ceramic products. It is also involved in the insurance and construction activities and assembly maintenance sectors. The company offers floor and wall tiles under the Seranova Seramik brand. It also operates chain stores and shopping malls in the retail sector under the name Anbera A.V.M. brand. In addition, the company is involved in the manufacturing and assembly of feed machines, steel constructions, soil processing facilities, manufactures machinery and steel constructions for ceramic factories, and manufactures ceramic molds. The company was founded in 1990 and is headquartered in Usak, Turkey.

stocks.name: ÜNLÜ Yatirim Holding A.S.
stocks.description: ÜNLÜ Yatirim Holding A.S. provides investment advisory and asset management services to investors, corporates, multinationals, and financial institutions in Turkey. It operates through Brokerage, Corporate Finance and Portfolio Management Services; Asset Management Consultancy and Services; Private Equity; and Investment Holding Services segments. The company offers investment services comprising corporate finance advisory, such as mergers and acquisitions, privatization consulting, and initial and secondary public offering; debt capital markets advisory consisting of foreign and local currency bond issuance, CLN, Eurobonds, private placements, convertible bonds, and asset-backed securities; and debt advisory, including acquisition and project finance, structured subordinated loans, and financial restructuring, as well as venture capital advisory; equity capital markets; loan capital markets and consultancy; and corporate equity sales services. It also provides capital markets services comprising corporate brokerage services, stock market placements, block sales/secondary public offering, fixed-income instruments, research, and treasury; and investment advisory and brokerage services, including investment advisory for capital markets, brokerage for stock exchange transactions, investment funds, fixed income securities, structured debt instruments, repo and Eurobond repo, over-the-counter derivatives, brokerage for hedging transactions and strategies, and IPO brokerage services. In addition, the company offers asset management services, such as non-performing loans management, including portfolio investments and restructuring; and fund and portfolio management services, such as investment funds and alternative investment funds. Further, it engages in the provision of financial consultancy and capital market intermediary services; and software and technology business. ÜNLÜ Yatirim Holding A.S. was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Usak Seramik Sanayi A.S.
stocks.description: Usak Seramik Sanayi A.S. engages in the production and sale of ceramics in Turkey, the United States, Germany, Italy, Canada, and internationally. It offers ceramic wall, floor, and granite tiles, kerb, decor, and porcelain, as well as borders products. The company was formerly known as Usak Elektro Porselen Sanayi A.S and changed its name to Usak Seramik Sanayi A.S. in 1986. The company was incorporated in 1972 and is headquartered in Banaz, Turkey.

stocks.name: Vakif Finansal Kiralama A.S.
stocks.description: Vakif Finansal Kiralama A.S. engages in the provision of financial leasing services in Turkey. The company was incorporated in 1988 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey. Vakif Finansal Kiralama A.S. is a subsidiary of Türkiye Vakiflar Bankasi Türk Anonim Ortakligi.

stocks.name: Vakko Tekstil ve Hazir Giyim Sanayi Isletmeleri A.S.
stocks.description: Vakko Tekstil ve Hazir Giyim Sanayi Isletmeleri A.S. manufactures and sells ready-to-wear clothes for men and women under the Vakko brand in Turkey. The company offers dresses, blouses, knitwear, jackets, skirts, pants, shorts, t-shirts and sweatshirts, trousers, and mont and kaban; jewelry, hats, belts, socks, bag accessories, beanies, and gloves; and scarves and shawls for women, as well as beach wear, swimwear, bikinis, sandals and slippers, and accessories. It also provides suits, jackets, knitwear, shirts, t-shirts, pants, shorts, outwear, tuxedos, underwear, beach wears, ties, pocket square, bow ties, handkerchiefs, belts, socks, bracelets, cufflinks, beanie, hats, gloves, and scarves for men; shoes and bags; home décor and textile products; chocolates; and cosmetics. The company offers products through its stores, as well as online under the name Vakko, Vakko Boutique, Vakkorama, VakkoWedding, VakkoHome, and VakkoFriends. Vakko Tekstil ve Hazir Giyim Sanayi Isletmeleri A.S. was founded in 1934 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey. Vakko Tekstil ve Hazir Giyim Sanayi Isletmeleri A.S. operates as a subsidiary of Vakko Holding A.S.

stocks.name: Vanet Gida Sanayi Iç Ve Dis Ticaret Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: Vanet Gida Sanayi Iç Ve Dis Ticaret Anonim Sirketi engages in the production, processing, purchase, and sales of various meat and meat products in Turkey. It provides sausage, salami, and fried meat products. The company was founded in 1977 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: VBT Yazilim Anonim Sirketi
stocks.description: VBT Yazilim Anonim Sirketi provides software, hardware, and consultancy services in Turkey. The company offers Heroty, an integrated human resources management platform; Flerpi commercial accounting software; e-transformation services; VizyonIK, a web-based payroll and human resources management software; and Information Processing Platforms. It also provides training, operating systems support, database support, information systems service management consultancy, project management, process consultancy services. The company was incorporated in 1993 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.

stocks.name: Verusaturk Girisim Sermayesi Yatirim Ortakligi A.S.
stocks.address: Maslak Mah. Saat Sk. Spine Tower Sitesi No:5
stocks.description: Verusaturk Girisim Sermayesi Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. is a private equity and venture capital firm specializing in bridge financing, recapitalizations, and growth capital investments. It prefers to invest in incubation, seed, early-mid-late venture, emerging growth, middle market, mature, turnaround, and later stage companies. The firm typically invests in following sectors: renewable energy, telecom, logistics, energy, technology and software, food, manufacturing, and mining. The firm prefers to invest in companies based in Turkey. The firm prefers to invest through its balance sheet investments. Verusaturk Girisim Sermayesi Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. was founded in January 09, 2012 and is based in Istanbul, Turkey.
